{"_id":"00fgzQICyyL8Ynj1","name":"Rotting Carapace","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/nature/tree-animated-stump-mushrooms-teal.webp","system":{"description":"Until this spell ends, you gain the following benefits:\n\n* **Layers of Fungus.** As a free action once per round, when you are dealt damage, you may halve the damage inflicted and deal **12 necrotic damage** to all creatures and objects within 10 feet of you.\n\n* **Towering.** Your Size increases by one category.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage increases by 4\\.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The radius of the damage of **Layers of Fungus** increases by 5 feet.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Self","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"10 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"You mold decaying bark and pungent fungus into a suit of armor.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage increases by 4\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The radius of the damage of **Layers of Fungus** increases by 5 feet.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"12","damageType":"necrotic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":166000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"09i3SXZzkHNL4QpE","name":"Forbidden Thought","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/perception/eye-slit-pink.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a basic **Quick-Wits** saving throw to resist **12d8 psychic damage**. On a failure, an affected creature cannot target you or your location until this spell ends. At the end of an affected creature's turn, they may retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success.\n\n**Contagion.** As a reaction when a creature affected by a spell effect with contagion trait dies, is knocked out, or burns a Resolve, you may cause a different target creature within range to become affected by the spell as if it had failed the saving throw. Newly affected creatures are not dealt the initial damage.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 4d8.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** On a failure, an affected creature cannot target a creature or the creature's location of your choice.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You bury a psychic hook into an enemy and pull them away from you.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Quick-Wits","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 4d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"On a failure, an affected creature cannot target a creature or the creature's location of your choice.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"12d8","damageType":"psychic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":155000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"0PrpUHrXk0XHUI8e","name":"Turn the Tide","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/wave-water-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You cause up to three target creatures within range to **regain 5d6 \\+ 5 ST** and gain the following additional benefits until this spell ends:\n\n* **A Door Opens.** All attacks they make have their critical strike threshold reduced by 2\\.\n\n* **Another Closes.** All attacks against them have their critical strike threshold increased by 2\\. If this would cause an attack's critical strike threshold to increase above 20, the attack instead cannot score a critical hit.\n\n**Expound.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins. If you do, you double the amount of ST regained for all affected creatures.\n\n***Heightening.*** When cast at 6th Circle, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* This spell's ST recovery die becomes 6d6 \\+ 6\\.","levelLabel":"5th Circle","spellLevel":6,"heightenedCircle":6,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"At the end of everything, stand tall.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery die becomes 6d6 \\+ 6\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":207000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"0pUBZAnQQ2FGuqOi","name":"Rectify Imperfection","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-etched-steel-blade.webp","system":{"description":"You choose a target weapon within range. All weapon attacks made with that weapon have their critical hit threshold reduced by 1 until this spell ends.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell's critical hit threshold reduction increases to 2\\.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You target an additional weapon within range.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Reach","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes or until you cast this spell again","concentration":false,"flavor":"Minor flaws in the process and materials can cause suboptimal weight distributions within a weapon.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's critical hit threshold reduction increases to 2\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"You target an additional weapon within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":81000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"1gHG4rWZL6ZCY6Bd","name":"Arc Spindle","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-spiral-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a target within range.\n\n**Expound.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins. If you do, you may designate up to two additional unique targets within 15 feet of any previous target.\n\nYou may use the **Expound** trait of **Arc Spindle** effects twice instead of only once. All targets must make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **2d8 lightning damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell's range becomes 60 feet and the maximum distance between unique targets becomes 30 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** Each usage of the **Expound** trait allows you to designate an additional unique target.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Electric strands coil around your arm as you bind the heartbeats of your foes with a fizzling shock.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"This spell's range becomes 60 feet and the maximum distance between unique targets becomes 30 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"Each usage of the **Expound** trait allows you to designate an additional unique target.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d8","damageType":"lightning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":37000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"1jcAbIEggT2YodZ6","name":"Venomous Malaise","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/death/skull-poison-green.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a **Fortitude** saving throw. On a failure, this spell beginsyou bestow a *malaise pool* of 5d8 to the target. As a free action once during each of your turns, you may deal **poison damage** to eachthe affected creature equal to a rolling of their malaise pool. Afterwards, malaise dice are retained in their pool unless their outcome was a 6, 7, or 8 (in which case they are discarded).\n\n**Contagion.** As a reaction when a creature affected by a spell effect with contagion trait dies, is knocked out, or burns a Resolve, you may cause a different target creature within range to become affected by the spell as if it had failed the saving throw. Doing so refills the malaise pool.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** The malaise pool begins with an additional 2d8.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** While affected by this spell, a creature is also poisoned. Removal or immunity to the condition also ends this spell.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** Malaise dice are only discarded when their outcome is an 8\\.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"Writhe within the confines of your frail composure.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The malaise pool begins with an additional 2d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"While affected by this spell, a creature is also poisoned. Removal or immunity to the condition also ends this spell.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"Malaise dice are only discarded when their outcome is an 8\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"malaise pool roll","damageType":"poison","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":141000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"1xuU5w9h2AIpj0fd","name":"Transmutation Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-glowing-triangle-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You create a 10 foot square originating from a target location within range that persists until this spell ends. The square typically stands upright but may be oriented however you wish. Any ranged weapon attack that targets through the square is *intercepted* and automatically misses. After intercepting five attacks, this spell ends.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** The square may now intercept ranged special attacks and ranged spell attacks.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The square may intercept eight attacks before it ends.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"square","shapeSize":"10 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You create a twisting barrier that turns arrows into doves.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The square may now intercept ranged special attacks and ranged spell attacks.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The square may intercept eight attacks before it ends.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":96000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2JKcJTemT1RFhhMB","name":"Ice Spires","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/barrier-ice-crystal-wall-jagged-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You create four *spires*, each of which appears in a target unoccupied 5 foot space within range and persists until this spell ends. A spire is a 15 foot tall Medium object that has 15 HP, an AC of 15 and a Toughness of 5\\. Creatures and objects that start their turn within 5 feet of a spire are slowed until the end of its turn.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You create two additional spires.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"Spires of ice pierce the earth and partially freeze those nearby.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"You create two additional spires.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":120000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2MJCJT1cDVKie5E5","name":"Command","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/control-influence-crown-gold.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a **Will** saving throw and speak a one-word command.\n\n**Expound.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins. If you do, you may target a second creature.\n\nThe command you speak may be any word you wish, and a creature that fails the saving throw must follow that command however it wishes on its next turn. Some examples of command words are provided below, and you are welcome to come up with your own:\n\n* **Drop.** The creature falls prone on their turn.\n\n* **Flee.** The creature attempts to end their turn further away from you by at least an amount equal to their Speed.\n\n* **Halt.** The creature does not move on their turn.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You may target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You wield your influence like a hammer hitting a nail.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Will","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You may target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":44000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2qs96qqboLsosWoQ","name":"Static Shock","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-hand-gray.webp","system":{"description":"You make a melee spell attack against a target within range. On a hit, the target is dealt **lightning damage** equal to your spellcasting modifier and loses a reaction if it had one.\n\n**Discharge.** You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the damage roll increases by **Xd12**, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Reach","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"You precisely overwhelm a nearby target with electricity.","attackType":"melee spell attack","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"spellcasting modifier","damageType":"lightning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":{"discharge_description":"Discharge. You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the damage roll increases by Xd12, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","discharge_damage":"Xd12"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":28000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2rYQPzCm5qgduaTn","name":"Invisibility","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/perception/shadow-stealth-eyes-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target within range to become invisible until this spell ends. If an affected creature attempts to inflict damage, apply a condition, or force another creature to make a saving throw in any way, this spell ends for them afterwards.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** Attempting to inflict damage, apply a condition, or force another creature to make a saving throw in any way no longer ends this spell.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell's duration becomes 1 hour.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"Reach","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You make someone or something disappear.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"Attempting to inflict damage, apply a condition, or force another creature to make a saving throw in any way no longer ends this spell.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"This spell's duration becomes 1 hour.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":122000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2smFx4Sa1b3a2gde","name":"Mirror Fate","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-large-white.webp","system":{"description":"Two target creatures within range must make a **Will** saving throw. If both creatures fail the saving throw, the two creatures are *fate-linked* to each other until this spell ends. A fate-linked creature suffers the following effects:\n\n* Whenever a fate-linked creature takes damage or regains ST, instead all fate-linked creatures take that amount of damage or ST recovery.\n\n* Conditions afflicting one fate-linked creature instead are applied to all fate-linked creatures.\n\nThis spell ends when either fate-linked creature dies or expends a Resolve, and the effect ends on both creatures if either effect ends.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell's saving throw DC is increased by 2\\.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You may target an additional creature within range. This spell ends if the effect ends for any of the fate-linked creatures.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"You tether the fates of two creatures: harm done to one does to the other.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Will","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's saving throw DC is increased by 2\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"You may target an additional creature within range. This spell ends if the effect ends for any of the fate-linked creatures.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":182000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2vXCbociClIO1Isi","name":"Crystalline Sentinel","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/ice-crystal-white.webp","system":{"description":"You conjure a *crystalline sentinel* at a target unoccupied space within range that persists until this spell ends. The crystalline sentinel is a Small object with 45 HP, 19 AC, 0 Toughness, advanced Hovering mobility, and a Speed of 30 feet. This spell ends early if it is destroyed.\n\n**Automaton.** You may issue the *commands* listed below to an object of your choice created by this spell by taking its listed kind of action. Each command may only be performed once per round:\n\n* **Counterspell (free action).** When you perceive a target cast a spell, you may cause the crystalline sentinel to cast **Counterspell** at 2nd Circle as a free action using your spellcasting modifier targeting the caster. Once the crystalline sentinel casts **Counterspell** three times, it is destroyed and this spell ends early.\n\n* **Move (free action during your turn).** The crystalline sentinel travels up to its Speed.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above, Repeatable)** The crystalline sentinel casts **Counterspell** at one Circle higher.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The crystalline sentinel may cast **Counterspell** one additional time before this spell ends.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"15 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You conjure an amalgam of quartz and magic to ward off hostile spells.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The crystalline sentinel casts **Counterspell** at one Circle higher.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The crystalline sentinel may cast **Counterspell** one additional time before this spell ends.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":148000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"33mVYVsbNrFSq88H","name":"Corrosion","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/acid/projectile-stream-bubbles.webp","system":{"description":"You make a ranged spell attack against a target within range. On a hit, the target is dealt **acid damage** equal to your spellcasting modifier and its AC is reduced by one guard step (their AC is either their Full Guard AC, Half Guard AC, or Base AC) until this spell ends.\n\n**Discharge.** You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the damage roll increases by **Xd10**, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"You launch a spray of weighted acid to melt away their defenses.","attackType":"ranged spell attack","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"spellcasting modifier","damageType":"acid","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":{"discharge_description":"Discharge. You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the damage roll increases by Xd10, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","discharge_damage":"Xd10"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":5000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"35RsxZhRdL2guzGn","name":"Sever Senses","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/perception/eye-tendrils-web-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You make a weapon attack.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make another weapon attack.\n\nBoth attacks have the following effects:\n\n* **If it hits**, the target is disoriented until the end of its next turn.\n\n* **If it hits a target that is already disoriented**, the attack deals an additional **2d8 psychic damage** to the target.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** If a target is dealt **psychic damage** by this spell, it also incurs disadvantage on its next **Quick-Wits** saving throw before the end of its next turn.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"None","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"A piercing delusion cuts the passage between perception and knowledge.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"If a target is dealt **psychic damage** by this spell, it also incurs disadvantage on its next **Quick-Wits** saving throw before the end of its next turn.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d8","damageType":"psychic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":84000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"35nwB3r0VZKt1weL","name":"Molasses Missile","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/nature/plant-poison-spit-green.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a target within range and create a *molasses missile* at your location that persists until this spell ends. At the end of each of your turns, the molasses missile travels 15 feet along the shortest path to the designated target. If no path exists, the molasses missile instead travels directly towards the target and impacts any obstruction on its path. Upon collision with the target or obstruction, the molasses missile deals **4d10 poison damage** and this spell ends.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage die increases by 4d10.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above, Repeatable)** The molasses missile now can dissolve through material while traveling at the same pace towards the target. It only stops if it collides with the target or an object with Toughness greater than 5\\. Choosing this enhancement multiple times increases the maximum Toughness by 5 for each selection after the first.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"120 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Indefinite","concentration":false,"flavor":"A meandering bubble of sizzling toxic goo that does not stop, does not sleep, and will always chase down its target to the ends of the earth.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage die increases by 4d10.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The molasses missile now can dissolve through material while traveling at the same pace towards the target. It only stops if it collides with the target or an object with Toughness greater than 5\\. Choosing this enhancement multiple times increases the maximum Toughness by 5 for each selection after the first.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"4d10","damageType":"poison","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":74000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"3VCSSOj3uhYTwdzk","name":"Subzero Spiker","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/projectile-ice-faceted-chunk.webp","system":{"description":"You summon a *subzero spiker* at a target unoccupied space within range that persists until this spell ends. The subzero spiker is a Tiny object with 15 HP, 15 AC, 5 Toughness, immunity to **cold damage**, advanced Hovering mobility, and a Speed of 15 feet. This spell ends early if it is destroyed.\n\n**Automaton.** You may issue the *commands* listed below to an object of your choice created by this spell by taking its listed kind of action. Each command may only be performed once per round:\n\n* **Ice Blast (action).** You deal **1d8 cold damage** to all creatures and objects within 15 feet of the subzero spiker.\n\n* **Move (free action during your turn).** The subzero spiker travels up to its Speed.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** The subzero spiker's HP increases by 15, its Toughness increases by 5, and this spell's damage roll increases by 1d8.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell's damage ignores DBs.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"A wizard's best friend: portable frigid spike grenade.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The subzero spiker's HP increases by 15, its Toughness increases by 5, and this spell's damage roll increases by 1d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"This spell's damage ignores DBs.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"1d8","damageType":"cold","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":91000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"3bCfp6hQgTGBW2Nb","name":"Abyssal Bleed","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/unholy/projectile-helix-blood-red.webp","system":{"description":"You designate three target creatures within range and mark them with *abyssal bleed* until this spell ends. If two creatures marked with abyssal bleed are within 10 feet of each other and one of them starts their turn, they and all creatures and objects within 5 feet of them take **1d6 necrotic damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 1d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell's damage now occurs when a creature marked with abyssal bleed starts their turn within 30 feet of another creature marked with abyssal bleed.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The abyssal bleed's damage radius becomes 10 feet.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You scream truths of eldritch malice and command them to scatter.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 1d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"This spell's damage now occurs when a creature marked with abyssal bleed starts their turn within 30 feet of another creature marked with abyssal bleed.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The abyssal bleed's damage radius becomes 10 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"1d6","damageType":"necrotic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":33000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"3irJnenG72vpgKb0","name":"Phosphorescence","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/orb-beams-green.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures and objects in a 15 foot radius sphere originating from a target location within range to be unable to gain the benefits of the invisible condition until this spell ends. Additionally, when you cast this spell, all affected creatures must make a **Reflex** saving throw. On a failure, all attacks made against them also gain advantage until this spell ends.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The radius of the area becomes 10 feet.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You coat an area with a faint, colorful glow.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The radius of the area becomes 10 feet.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":78000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"3sf1FSqHaX1xyBLR","name":"Twin Parallax","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/defensive/illusion-evasion-echo-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You cause up to two target creatures within range to **regain** **10d4 \\+ 10 ST** and become *parallaxed* until this spell ends. When a *parallaxed* creature takes the Dodge action on their turn, the next attack made against them before this spell ends automatically misses.\n\n***Heightening.*** When cast at 6th Circle, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* This spell's ST recovery roll increases to 12d4 \\+ 12\\.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** You target up to four creatures within range.\n\n# **List of 6th Circle Spells**","levelLabel":"5th Circle","spellLevel":6,"heightenedCircle":6,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"They truly are seeing double.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases to 12d4 \\+ 12\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"You target up to four creatures within range.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":208000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"4JGJnAsmmEURfEFL","name":"Herald of Defiance","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/holy/angel-winged-humanoid-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You grant up to three target allies within range DB 5 against **radiant** and **necrotic damage** until this spell ends. When an affected creature is dealt **necrotic damage**, the source of the damage is dealt **5 radiant damage**. Likewise, when an affected creature is dealt **radiant damage**, the source of the damage is dealt **5 necrotic damage**. \n\nA creature may be dealt damage by **Herald of Defiance** at most once per turn.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** Both this spell's DB and its damage increase by 5\\.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"When the forces of life and death overflow, you are there to turn back the tide.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"Both this spell's DB and its damage increase by 5\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"You target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"5","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":118000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"4qSCakvvyt9HY61w","name":"DР\"В©jР\"В  Vwoop","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/time/arrows-circling-pink.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a basic **Quick-Wits** saving throw to resist **12d6 psychic damage**. On a failure, during the target's next turn, they must repeat an action of your choosing that they performed on their previous turn. If the creature has not taken a turn yet, they instead must take a Move action to travel up to their Speed in the direction they came from or away from where you entered the combat.\n\nIf the creature has not taken a turn yet, this additional effect does not occur.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 4d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** On a failed save, the target repeats an action that you have already taken during this turn rather than an action they took.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You forcibly push back a creature's thought process by six seconds.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Quick-Wits","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 4d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"On a failed save, the target repeats an action that you have already taken during this turn rather than an action they took.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"12d6","damageType":"psychic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":150000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"5ctpgA1fO0LbJEkL","name":"Resistance","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-glowing-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 15 foot radius sphere originating from a target location within range. All creatures in the area **regain 2d6 \\+ 2 ST** and gain advantage on the next saving throw they make before this spell ends.\n\n**Expound.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins. If you do, you double the amount of ST regained for all affected creatures.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d6 \\+ 1\\.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** You may choose any number of creatures in this spell's area to be unaffected.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"Steeled for the darkest hour.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d6 \\+ 1\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"You may choose any number of creatures in this spell's area to be unaffected.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":127000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"5fMUDMMyNcXw7GEA","name":"Summon Piano","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/sonic/bell-alarm-red-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You conjure a *piano* at a target location within range that persists until this spell ends. The piano is a Large object with 30 HP, 10 AC, and 5 Toughness. This spell ends if it is destroyed. You gain advantage on CHA checks performed while playing the piano. If the piano falls, all creatures and objects underneath it, as well as the piano itself, must make a basic **Poise** saving throw to resist **4d6 bludgeoning damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** You summon a pipe organ instead, which increases its Size to Huge with 40 HP, 5 AC, and 15 Toughness.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Hour","concentration":false,"flavor":"And now, the grand finale\\!","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Poise","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"You summon a pipe organ instead, which increases its Size to Huge with 40 HP, 5 AC, and 15 Toughness.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"4d6","damageType":"bludgeoning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":137000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"5riM0qIbox1CJKe5","name":"Ragnarok","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/beam-strike-village-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 60 foot radius sphere centered in a target location within range. When you cast this spell, and at the end of each of your next two turns, creatures within the sphere are subjected to a series of effects:\n\n* **When cast:** A giant, radiant blade falls from the sky, causing all creatures within the area to make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **6d10 radiant damage**. Until the end of your next turn, Divine spells cast in this spell's area have their casting time shortened by one action and cost twice the Spell Points.\n\n* **At the end of your first subsequent turn:** Fire erupts from the earth, causing all creatures standing on a surface in the area to make a **Reflex** saving throw to resist **6d10 fire damage**. All creatures and objects in the area are set ablaze for the duration of this spell. Until the end of your next turn, Divine spells cannot be cast within the area.\n\n* **At the end of your second subsequent turn:** Rain falls within the area, causing all creatures within the area to regain **9d6 ST**, and this spell ends.","levelLabel":"6th Circle","spellLevel":7,"heightenedCircle":7,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"3 actions","range":"90 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"60 feet","duration":"2 Rounds","concentration":false,"flavor":"Divine forces war, perish, and rise again.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"6d10","damageType":"radiant","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":219000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6KodqYYZcQAqMRFt","name":"Smoldering Crown","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/control-influence-crown-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a basic **Will** saving throw to resist **2d6 fire damage.** On a failure, the creature is *crowned* by this spell until this spell ends. On each of your future turns, as a free action, you may deal **2d10 fire damage** to creatures crowned by this spell provided you can target them within the range of this spell.\n\n**Contagion.** As a reaction when a creature affected by a spell effect with contagion trait dies, is knocked out, or burns a Resolve, you may cause a different target creature within range to become affected by the spell as if it had failed the saving throw. Newly affected creatures are not dealt the initial damage.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's initial damage roll increases by 2d6 and the crowned damage roll increases by 1d10.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell's damage ignores DBs.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** You target two creatures within range.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"A damned crown of flames for thee.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Will","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's initial damage roll increases by 2d6 and the crowned damage roll increases by 1d10.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"This spell's damage ignores DBs.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You target two creatures within range.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d6","damageType":"fire","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":88000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"6rQCaGGFRdoWwa3m","name":"Labyrinthine Marble","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/circled-gem-pink.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures within a 10 foot radius sphere originating from a target location within range to be teleported into a demiplane known as a *maze plane*. Additionally, a Tiny marble with 50 HP, 20 AC, and 25 Toughness appears at the target location. This marble contains the maze plane and this spell ends if it is broken. Additionally, the marble is surprisingly heavy, requiring a DC 20 STR effort check to lift, carry, push, or pull it.\n\nWhen a creature trapped in a maze plane starts their turn, they may make an INT effort check and add the result to a running score. If multiple creatures travel together, only one creature makes the INT effort check for the whole group. Once a creature surpasses a threshold score of 50, they reach the boundaries of the maze and may inflict damage upon or take Wreck an Object actions against the marble from the inside.\n\nWhen this spell ends, all creatures trapped in the maze plane are ejected onto the nearest unoccupied spaces from the marble's location.","levelLabel":"6th Circle","spellLevel":7,"heightenedCircle":7,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"10 feet","duration":"Indefinite","concentration":false,"flavor":"You trap your foes into a maze of your own twisting design encased within a small marble.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":214000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"7cmuTlR7pVtmbffb","name":"Sacred Geometry","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-pentagon-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 60 foot radius circle originating from a target location within range and then create three 5 foot wide 120 foot long lines originating from a point on the edge of the circle. All creatures and objects in the sphere must make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **10d6 radiant damage**. Creatures inside both the sphere and one of the lines are immune to the damage from this spell and instead regain **10d6 ST**.\n\n***Heightening.*** When cast at 6th Circle, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* This spell's damage and healing roll both become 12d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** You invert the effect of this spell: creatures in the circle regain ST while creatures both in the circle and in one of the lines must make the basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist the damage of this spell.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** You create a fourth line.","levelLabel":"5th Circle","spellLevel":6,"heightenedCircle":6,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"60 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Any two points make a line.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage and healing roll both become 12d6.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"You invert the effect of this spell: creatures in the circle regain ST while creatures both in the circle and in one of the lines must make the basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist the damage of this spell.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"You create a fourth line.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"10d6","damageType":"radiant","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":204000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"7xBbq0Ig4X69AFey","name":"Compound Deconstruction","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/acid/projectile-beams-salvo-green.webp","system":{"description":"You make a weapon attack.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make another weapon attack.\n\nBoth attacks have the following effects:\n\n* **If the target has previously taken acid damage this turn**, the attack gains advantage.\n\n* **If it hits,** you deal **2d6 acid damage** to the target and all creatures and objects in a 5 foot wide, 10 foot long line originating from the target.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll for each attack increases by 1d6.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The line's length becomes 20 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"None","shape":"line","shapeSize":"10 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"This particular flavor of alchemy is classified as \"quantifiable disaster.\"","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll for each attack increases by 1d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The line's length becomes 20 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d6","damageType":"acid","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":107000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8XNSj58YZdmCQVQy","name":"Prismatic Blast","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/elements-air-earth-fire-water.webp","system":{"description":"You make a ranged spell attack against a target within range. On a hit, the target is dealt **damage** equal to your spellcasting modifier. Roll a d4 to determine the attack's damage type: 1 is **acid**, 2 is **cold**, 3 is **fire**, and 4 is **lightning**.\n\n**Discharge.** You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, If you do, the damage roll increases by **Xd8**, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You envision a reality without limits. A rainbow without ends.","attackType":"ranged spell attack","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"spellcasting modifier","damageType":"prismaticblast","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":{"discharge_description":"Discharge. You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, If you do, the damage roll increases by Xd8, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","discharge_damage":"Xd8"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":19000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8og1vKOfl6si4lye","name":"Golden Blade","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/swords-light-glowing-white.webp","system":{"description":"You make a melee spell attack against a target within range. On a hit, the target is dealt **radiant damage** equal to your spellcasting modifier.\n\n**Discharge.** You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the following effects occur:\n\n* **Bonus Damage.** The damage roll increases by **Xd10**, where X is half your Tier Bonus.\n\n* **Uplift.** You may designate a target ally other than yourself within 30 feet of you and grant them advantage on the next attack check they make before this spell ends.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Reach","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"You form a blade of heavenly starlight with a sharpness cutting through your foes and breaking the reins of fate itself.","attackType":"melee spell attack","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"spellcasting modifier","damageType":"radiant","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":{"discharge_description":"Discharge. You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the following effects occur: Bonus Damage. The damage roll increases by Xd10, where X is half your Tier Bonus. Uplift. You may designate a target ally other than yourself within 30 feet of you and grant them advantage on the next attack check they make before this spell ends.","discharge_damage":"Xd10"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":11000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9EzIFOYWnssmrI4G","name":"Disguise","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/mask-metal-silver-white.webp","system":{"description":"You change the appearance of a target creature within range to a new one of your choosing until this spell ends. This effect may include altering the appearance of worn clothing and equipment, the coloration and texture of skin, the placement and appearance of appendages on one's body (such as arms, legs, eyes, ears, or tails; any appendages removed with this spell are instead invisible), and stature, though this spell may not alter a creature's Size.\n\nSpell effects with the **Sensor** trait identify affected creatures according to their new appearance from this spell.\n\n**Illusion.** This spell effect is intangible but creatures perceive it as real until they attempt to physically interact with it. As an action, a creature that **perceives** this effect may make a **Quick-Wits** saving throw. On a success, the effect becomes obviously illusory to them.\t\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell may now also alter an affected creature's voice as a part of their new appearance.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** An affected creature may take an action to change their appearance again to a new one of their choosing.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** This spell may now alter an affected creature's apparent Size by one category larger or smaller.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 minute","range":"Reach","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Until the end of your next short or long rest","concentration":false,"flavor":"If you plan to get into trouble, you should at least fit in.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Quick-Wits","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell may now also alter an affected creature's voice as a part of their new appearance.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"An affected creature may take an action to change their appearance again to a new one of their choosing.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"This spell may now alter an affected creature's apparent Size by one category larger or smaller.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":47000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9HuStpcCuuw4dXmh","name":"Anathemic Release","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/life/cross-explosion-burst-green.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 15 foot diameter sphere originating from a target location within range. All creatures in the area **regain 6d6 \\+ 6 ST** and are cleansed of all conditions and effects of the target's choosing.\n\n**Expound.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins. If you do, you double the amount of ST regained for all affected creatures.","levelLabel":"6th Circle","spellLevel":7,"heightenedCircle":7,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"The hated form is destroyed, the one unbound set in its place.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":209000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9dguC7wD3jwJEPhd","name":"Temporary Truce","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/holy/yin-yang-balance-symbol.webp","system":{"description":"You cause any number of target creatures within range to become pacified until this spell ends. If an affected creature perceives another creature doing anything hostile, such as attacking, grappling, or casting a harmful spell, this spell ends early.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"3 actions","range":"120 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"Can everyone just stop for a second?","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":94000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9mgcQOo6sQJkU284","name":"Polymorph","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/silhouette-grow-shrink-tan.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a **Will** saving throw. A creature gains a degree of advantage on the saving throw for each Resolve they have remaining. On a failure, a target is polymorphed into a Tier 0 beast creature of your choosing until this spell ends. While polymorphed in this manner, burning a Resolve does not expend it.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell's duration is extended to last until you take a long rest.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Hour","concentration":true,"flavor":"You transform a creature into a harmless animal.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Will","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's duration is extended to last until you take a long rest.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":164000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"A14aV0N8B7oHbeoP","name":"Gnarled Garden","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/nature/tree-roots-glow-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 30 foot cube originating from a target location within range that persists until this spell ends. All surface spaces within the cube are difficult terrain. Additionally, once per round until this spell ends, you may take an action to cause a target creature in the cube to **regain 4d6 \\+ 4 ST**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 2d6 \\+ 2\\.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** Creatures of your choosing may ignore the difficult terrain caused by this spell.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** When you take the action for this spell to grant ST recovery, you may move the origin of the cube up to 15 feet to a new target location within range. This movement of the cube may occur before or after granting the ST recovery.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"cube","shapeSize":"30 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"A mass of knotted overgrowth envelopes the battlefield, bearing fruit to those you wish to protect.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 2d6 \\+ 2\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"Creatures of your choosing may ignore the difficult terrain caused by this spell.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"When you take the action for this spell to grant ST recovery, you may move the origin of the cube up to 15 feet to a new target location within range. This movement of the cube may occur before or after granting the ST recovery.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":117000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ACkFV5oCDwlIXZf7","name":"Earthen Wall","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/earth/barrier-stone-brown-green.webp","system":{"description":"You create a wall that is 5 feet thick, 10 feet tall, and 30 feet wide whose endpoints are target surfaces within range. The wall may be bent and curved at your choosing, and may even be formed into a ring with an inner radius of 5 feet. Each 5 foot length section of the wall has 15 HP, an AC of 10, and 5 Toughness. Creatures are capable of climbing the wall.\n\nWhen this spell ends, all sections of the wall crumble to dust.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above, Repeatable)** The wall's height is increased by 5 feet and its Toughness is increased by 5\\.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The wall's length is increased by 30 feet and can be formed into a circle with a radius 5 feet longer. Each section's HP is also increased by 10\\.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You awaken the local tectonics to raise a barrier of soil and stone.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The wall's height is increased by 5 feet and its Toughness is increased by 5\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The wall's length is increased by 30 feet and can be formed into a circle with a radius 5 feet longer. Each section's HP is also increased by 10\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":54000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ATAwMN30kxvSl4wP","name":"Poison Needles","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/acid/projectile-needles-salvo-green.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures and objects in a cone in front of you whose length is the range of this spell to make a basic **Fortitude** saving throw to resist **2d8 poison damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** On a failure, an affected creature is poisoned until the end of its next turn.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** You create a second cone originating from your location whose length is the range of this spell. A creature or object cannot be affected by an instance of this spell more than once.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"15 feet","shape":"cone","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You throw a barrage of envenomed needles.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"On a failure, an affected creature is poisoned until the end of its next turn.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"You create a second cone originating from your location whose length is the range of this spell. A creature or object cannot be affected by an instance of this spell more than once.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d8","damageType":"poison","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":79000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"AXAyEZrJBRBLllZo","name":"Heat Sink","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/barrier-shield-explosion-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"You conjure a *heat sink* at a target unoccupied space within range. The heat sink is a Small object with 45 HP, 15 AC, 15 Toughness, advanced Climbing mobility, and a Speed of 30 feet. This spell ends early if it is destroyed.\n\nIf the heat sink is within a creature's Reach, they may take an action to *disarm* it, ending this spell. When this spell ends without the heat sink being disarmed, all creatures and unattended objects within 30 feet of it must make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **30 fire damage**.\n\n**Automaton.** You may issue the *commands* listed below to an object of your choice created by this spell by taking its listed kind of action. Each command may only be performed once per round:\n\n* **Absorb (free action).** When one or more allies within 30 feet of the heat sink are dealt **fire damage**, you may redirect half of the total damage dealt to the heat sink. \n\n* **Move (free action during your turn).** The heat sink travels up to its Speed.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** You choose an elemental damage type other than **fire**. The damage type the heat sink may **Absorb** as well as the damage dealt by this spell is now the chosen damage type.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The heat sink's HP increases by 15 and its Toughness increases by 5\\.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"\"Do I cut the striped wire or the checkered one?\"","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"You choose an elemental damage type other than **fire**. The damage type the heat sink may **Absorb** as well as the damage dealt by this spell is now the chosen damage type.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The heat sink's HP increases by 15 and its Toughness increases by 5\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"30","damageType":"fire","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":158000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"AjqmNJZHc6SKcFxR","name":"Into the Fold","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/movement/portal-vortex-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You cause up to five willing creatures to teleport to an unoccupied space within your Reach and **regain 6d8 \\+ 12 ST**. A creature must be on the same plane of existence as you to be affected by this spell.","levelLabel":"6th Circle","spellLevel":7,"heightenedCircle":7,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Unlimited","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Yeah, I'm thinking we're back.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":213000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Ap5SLLW1MoQdSzuq","name":"Iron Skin","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/defensive/armor-shield-barrier-steel.webp","system":{"description":"You grant a target willing creature within range the following effects until this spell ends:\n\n* **Alloyed.** They gain DB 10 against **physical damage**.\n\n* **Conductive.** Once per turn when they take **lightning damage**, they and any creatures touching them (such as by being grappled or carried) are dealt an additional **5 lightning damage**.\n\n* **Heavy.** Their Speed is reduced by 5 feet and they are unable to swim, climb, jump, or fly.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** An affected creature gains advantage on **Poise** saving throws and all STR combat checks made against an affected creature incur disadvantage.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell's range becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** This spell's DB increases by 5\\.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"They can walk, but if they move, they might fall.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"An affected creature gains advantage on **Poise** saving throws and all STR combat checks made against an affected creature incur disadvantage.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"This spell's range becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"This spell's DB increases by 5\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"5","damageType":"lightning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":67000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"AtecE6iI6efeY4m6","name":"Spectral Lantern","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/light-lantern-lit-white.webp","system":{"description":"You summon a *spectral lantern* at a target location within range that persists until this spell ends. The spectral lantern is an object that has HP equal to 5 x your Tier Bonus, 15 AC, 10 Toughness, a Speed equal to this spell's range, and advanced Hovering mobility. This spell ends early if the spectral lantern is destroyed or you cast **Spectral Lantern** again. The spectral lantern illuminates its surroundings.\n\nAs an object interaction, you may cause the spectral lantern to travel up its Speed. This spell ends early if the spectral lantern is ever further than four times this spell's range from you.\n\n**Scrying.** As an action, you may choose an object created by this spell and begin perceiving as if you were located at it. As a free action, you may end this effect. While perceiving in this manner, you are always **aware** of subjects within 15 feet of the object and are **uncertain** of all subjects beyond this distance.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"1 Hour","concentration":false,"flavor":"You bind a portion of your soul into a lantern and let it fly. It is you, and it shall light the way.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":26000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"B7MLbtBg9uFxuibC","name":"Heart of the Storm","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-explosion-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to gain the following benefits:\n\n* **Cleansing.** The target is cleansed of the incapacitated, stunned and frozen conditions.\n\n* **Recovery.** The target **regains 24d6 ST**. For each d6 rolled whose outcome is a 6, the d6 *explodes* and you add an additional d6 to the ST recovery roll. All d6s added to the ST recovery roll may also explode if their outcome is a 6\\.\n\n* **Explosion.** Creatures of your choosing within 15 feet of the target must make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **lightning damage** equal to 5 x the number of d6s that exploded.","levelLabel":"6th Circle","spellLevel":7,"heightenedCircle":7,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"120 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"A bolt of lightning strikes an ally with explosive resurgence.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"5 x exploded d6s","damageType":"lightning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":212000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Ba3VLE0OGq6zg1Ja","name":"Magicnetic Needle","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/projectile-needles-salvo-white.webp","system":{"description":"You make a ranged spell attack against a target within range. You gain advantage on the attack check if the target is concentrating on an effect. On a hit, the target is dealt **force damage** equal to your spellcasting modifier.\n\n**Discharge.** You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, you may increase the damage roll by **Xd8**, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"A silvered arrow to your greatest foe: other wizards.","attackType":"ranged spell attack","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"spellcasting modifier","damageType":"force","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":{"discharge_description":"Discharge. You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, you may increase the damage roll by Xd8, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","discharge_damage":"Xd8"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":14000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"BtLzyrV8sSFdJftH","name":"Cubify","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/squares-3d-green.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target Tiny or Small unattended object within range to become polymorphed into a Tiny object with 5 HP, 15 AC, and 5 Toughness until this spell ends. This new form does not retain any characteristics or features from the target's original form except for its weight. This spell ends early if the new form is destroyed.\n\nYou choose the new form the first time you ever cast **Cubify**. Each time you cast **Cubify** thereafter, the new form must be exactly identical to what you chose the first time.\n\nA creature guessing the identity of an object polymorphed by **Cubify** based on the weight they feel while holding it may be able to confirm their guess upon succeeding a DC 15 INT effort or trade check.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Reach","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Indefinite","concentration":false,"flavor":"Turning everything into completely featureless cubes allows for much more efficient packing.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":6000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"BznTPbcvxyNaTjeL","name":"Lucidity","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/holy/meditation-chi-focus-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 15 foot radius sphere originating from a target location within range. All creatures in the area **regain 2d6 \\+ 2 ST** and are both cleansed of and immune to being disoriented until this spell ends.\n\n**Expound.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins. If you do, you double the amount of ST regained for all affected creatures.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d6 \\+ 1\\.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The radius of this spell's area becomes 25 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"You break the clouding of senses with piercing clarity.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d6 \\+ 1\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The radius of this spell's area becomes 25 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":125000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"CSVrDvGonH2KzUo2","name":"Illusion","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/mask-metal-silver-white.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 10 foot cube originating at a target location within range and create a static image within the area that persists until this spell ends. The visual appearance of this image may take on any form of your choosing, but cannot create any sound or other sensory effect.\n\n**Illusion.** This spell effect is intangible but creatures perceive it as real until they attempt to physically interact with it. As an action, a creature that **perceives** this effect may make a **Quick-Wits** saving throw. On a success, the effect becomes obviously illusory to them.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** The effect may now also include sounds and other sensory effects. These effects are perceptible outside of this spell's area.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The visual appearance may now be animated, though this animation must be determined when this spell begins. As an action, you may move the origin point of this spell's area up to 30 feet to a location you are **aware** of.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The side length of the cube increases by 10 feet. Additionally, you may cause the casting time of this spell to be 1 minute to multiply the resulting total side length by 3\\.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"cube","shapeSize":"10 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"What you see is not always what you get.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Quick-Wits","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The effect may now also include sounds and other sensory effects. These effects are perceptible outside of this spell's area.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The visual appearance may now be animated, though this animation must be determined when this spell begins. As an action, you may move the origin point of this spell's area up to 30 feet to a location you are **aware** of.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The side length of the cube increases by 10 feet. Additionally, you may cause the casting time of this spell to be 1 minute to multiply the resulting total side length by 3\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":66000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Cf8OHFX3mAwjd3Ms","name":"Lightning Link","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/lightning/projectile-tendrils-teal.webp","system":{"description":"You make a weapon attack.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make another weapon attack. This second attack ignores weapon attack fatigue.\n\nIf both attacks hit, a 5 foot wide line subsequently forms with endpoints that are the locations of the targets of the two attacks. You deal **3d10 lightning damage** to all creatures and objects in the area. Afterwards, the targets of the two attacks are pulled 5 feet towards each other and become prone.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 1d10.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** If the targets are pulled into adjacent spaces, they become stuck to each other until the targets take an action on the same turn to cleanse the condition.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The pull distance for both targets becomes 10 feet.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"None","shape":"line","shapeSize":"Variable","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You braid kinetic and electrical forces into a transmutational chain.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 1d10.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"If the targets are pulled into adjacent spaces, they become stuck to each other until the targets take an action on the same turn to cleanse the condition.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The pull distance for both targets becomes 10 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"3d10","damageType":"lightning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":161000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"CvFgkKpZVVGV9xht","name":"Spark of Hope","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-cross-strong-green.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to **regain ST** equal to your spellcasting modifier.\n\n**Expound.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins. If you do, the ST recovery roll increases by **Xd6**, where X is half your Tier Bonus. If the target is frightened, this spell's ST recovery roll is replaced with the maximum possible total.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"A spark in the darkness to keep the fire burning.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":25000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"CyQqJdHKKXQIuz8O","name":"Armor of Souls","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/holy/barrier-shield-winged-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You grant up to three target allies within range their Half Guard AC until this spell ends. If at any point all affected creatures have their Full Guard AC simultaneously, this spell is *upgraded* for all affected creatures until this spell ends.\n\nWhile this spell is upgraded, critical hits against any affected creature are negated and instead count as a normal hit.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"The souls of those who love you continue to protect you.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"You target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":38000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"DOGwzHNdeyeLky5i","name":"Cold Snap","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/projectile-ice-teardrop.webp","system":{"description":"You make a ranged spell attack against a target within range. On a hit, the target is dealt **cold damage** equal to your spellcasting modifier and is slowed until this spell ends.\n\n**Discharge.** You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the damage roll increases by **Xd8**, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"Frigid air dances about your focus before concentrating into a chilled blast.","attackType":"ranged spell attack","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"spellcasting modifier","damageType":"cold","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":{"discharge_description":"Discharge. You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the damage roll increases by Xd8, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","discharge_damage":"Xd8"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":4000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"DeMjl0ZTkaNwj1kN","name":"Bristle Lash","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/nature/root-vine-thorned-coil-green.webp","system":{"description":"You make a ranged spell attack against a target within range. On a hit, the target is dealt **piercing damage** equal to your spellcasting modifier.\n\n**Discharge.** You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the target is pulled 10 feet towards you and the damage roll increases by **Xd6**, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"A thorny vine wraps around an enemy and draws them in.","attackType":"ranged spell attack","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"spellcasting modifier","damageType":"piercing","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":{"discharge_description":"Discharge. You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the target is pulled 10 feet towards you and the damage roll increases by Xd6, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","discharge_damage":"Xd6"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":3000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"E6MCEbhfKxO1IHlP","name":"Ascendant Wings","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/buff-flight-wings-runes-red-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"You grant basic Flying mobility to up to three target allies within range until this spell ends. If at any point all affected creatures become more than 30 feet above the ground, this spell is *upgraded* for all affected creatures until this spell ends.\n\nWhile this spell is upgraded and an affected creature is more than 30 feet above the ground, they may take an action to fall down to the ground, take no falling damage, and cause all other creatures and objects within 10 feet of them to make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **3d6 fire damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 1d6.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** You grant all affected creatures advanced Flying mobility.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"Flaming wings sprout from your backs and carry you aloft.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 1d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"You grant all affected creatures advanced Flying mobility.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"3d6","damageType":"fire","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":145000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"EJMciRQPSzHtBNqf","name":"Cloak","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/perception/silhouette-stealth-shadow.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target Large or smaller creature or object within range to gain the **Stealthy** trait from the invisible condition until this spell ends, granting them advantage on ability checks made to cause **intrigued** sentries to return to being **relaxed**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** You may choose for the casting of this spell to be imperceptible.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell's casting time becomes 3 actions and its range becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You may target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 minute","range":"Reach","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Until the end of your next short or long rest","concentration":true,"flavor":"The eyes refuse to focus on the shrouded form, the mind compensating for the missing space.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"You may choose for the casting of this spell to be imperceptible.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"This spell's casting time becomes 3 actions and its range becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You may target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":43000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"F33FuVujJMNxNx1x","name":"Never Mind","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/hypnosis-mesmerism-watch.webp","system":{"description":"You may choose for the casting of this spell to be imperceptible. You may cast this spell as a reaction immediately after saying something up to the length of a sentence. You cause a target creature to make a **Will** saving throw. You do not learn the total of the check. On a failure, an affected creature forgets what you said. On a success, they learn that you cast this spell on them.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 reaction","range":"None","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Please ignore that.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Will","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":75000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FBxVQXMvSe5pxElO","name":"Reunmagnification","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/silhouette-grow-shrink-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target within range to make a **Fortitude** saving throw. Objects of Size Medium or smaller automatically fail this saving throw. On a failure, two things occur:\n\n* **Unlarge.** The target becomes one Size smaller until this spell ends.\n\n* **Enlarge.** You cause a second target within range to become one Size larger until this spell ends.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"Conservation of magnification dictates an equilibrium despite your attempts to disturb it.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":128000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FO5ulfp0wIkKb2ta","name":"Drowsiness","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/sleep-bubble-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You cause up to three target creatures within range to become slowed. Creatures that are immune to being charmed are not affected by this spell.\n\n**Drowsiness** effects have the **Out of It** condition trait, which means they end early for a creature if it takes any damage or if they are within another creature's Reach and that creature takes an action to shake them out of their stupor.\n\nA creature under the effect of the **Drowsiness** spell incurs disadvantage on saving throws imposed by the **Sleep** spell.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You may target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Indefinite","concentration":false,"flavor":"You begin to metronomically count upwards. A hypnosis as old as time itself.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You may target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":52000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FVoazyBQDGMIl7mk","name":"Life Ball","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-area-circle-red-green.webp","system":{"description":"You conjure a *life ball* represented as a target 5 foot space within range that persists until this spell ends. Whenever an ally is within a life ball's space for the first time since the start of your most recent turn, they **regain 1d81d4 \\+ 1 ST.**\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d81d4 \\+ 1\\.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** If a life ball is within the Reach of an ally, they may take an action to relocate the life ball to a new 5 foot space they target within this spell's range of them.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You conjure an additional life ball at a target 5 foot space within range.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"Ball is life.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d81d4 \\+ 1\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"If a life ball is within the Reach of an ally, they may take an action to relocate the life ball to a new 5 foot space they target within this spell's range of them.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You conjure an additional life ball at a target 5 foot space within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":69000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Fn9Og6Ss4uCAfPuz","name":"Momentary Stupor","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/hypnosis-mesmerism-eye.webp","system":{"description":"You make a ranged spell attack against a target within range. On a hit, the target takes **psychic damage** equal to your spellcasting modifier and incurs disadvantage on the next attack check they make before this spell ends.\n\n**Discharge.** You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the damage roll increases by **Xd6**, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"You fire a psychic ray that causes the foe to take a moment to collect themselves.","attackType":"ranged spell attack","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"spellcasting modifier","damageType":"psychic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":{"discharge_description":"Discharge. You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the damage roll increases by Xd6, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","discharge_damage":"Xd6"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":17000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"FpL2UpkSGfd0w9Jq","name":"Mending","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/cog-glowing-green.webp","system":{"description":"You heal all missing HP of a target Small or smaller object within range whose Toughness is less than or equal to 5 x half your Tier Bonus.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Reach","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You help recall an object's younger memories.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":15000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GAeQEiz8hKk2ZAWq","name":"Corpse Bomb","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-explode-disintegrate.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target undead creature within range to make a basic **Fortitude** saving throw to resist **4d8 force damage**. If the target diesis brought to 0 HP and no Resolve from by this spell's initial damage, they explode and deal **2d6 force damage** to all creatures and objects within 10 feet of it.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's target damage roll increases by 4d8 and the explosion damage roll increases by 2d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** Any undead creature that dies from brought to 0 HP and no Resolve by an explosion from this spell also explode.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Undeath prides itself on its perpetuity. You remind them of the fragile balance of vital forces at play.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's target damage roll increases by 4d8 and the explosion damage roll increases by 2d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"Any undead creature that dies from brought to 0 HP and no Resolve by an explosion from this spell also explode.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"4d8","damageType":"force","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":45000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"GxvSSAHXE8MXIo9X","name":"Bless","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/buff-luck-fortune-gold.webp","system":{"description":"You grant up to three target creatures within range a \\+5 bonus to all attack and combat checks they make until this spell ends.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You bring good fortune to the troubles that await you.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"You target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":174000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"H9UUpQ7LB2NgmPbl","name":"Erupting Flame","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/explosion-fireball-medium-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 15 foot radius, 15 foot tall cylinder originating from a target surface within range. At the start of your next turn, all creatures and objects in the area must make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **2d6 fire damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** All unoccupied surface spaces in the area are set ablaze. Any creatures affected by this spell that fail the **Reflex** saving throw are also set ablaze.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"cylinder","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You cause a section of ground to slowly heat up before suddenly exploding with gouts of flame.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"All unoccupied surface spaces in the area are set ablaze. Any creatures affected by this spell that fail the **Reflex** saving throw are also set ablaze.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d6","damageType":"fire","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":57000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HHszBXuQi2zbl6VV","name":"Fan of Flames","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/blast-jet-stream-embers-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures and objects in a cone in front of you whose length is the range of this spell to make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **3d6 fire damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 3d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell's damage ignores DBs.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 40 feet.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"20 feet","shape":"cone","shapeSize":"20 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"A pyral fan of flames explodes out of the palms of your hands.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 3d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"This spell's damage ignores DBs.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 40 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"3d6","damageType":"fire","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":58000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HS2Ek9bjFp4B1kXK","name":"Ancient Reading","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-carved-stone-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a target within range. If it is a symbol of some kind, you learn its true meaning. If it is a passage of text written in an ancient or dead language, you may read it.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"The knowledge of yore shall be held by the minds of the living.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":1000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HcotO0Dx5mLfvNLp","name":"Wildfire Strike","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-wave-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"You set all surface spaces and creatures ablaze in a 5 foot wide line in front of you whose length is the range of this spell.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make a weapon attack. If the attack hits a target that is ablaze, it deals an additional **2d4 fire damage** to the target.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d4.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 30 feet.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"15 feet","shape":"line","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Streaks of flame erupt from your weapons with ashen might.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d4.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 30 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d4","damageType":"fire","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":99000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Hh5Ow53OiTjECwT4","name":"Unraveling Mark","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/unholy/hand-marked-pink.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target within range to be dealt an additional **1d8 force damage** on the next three attacks that hit it before this spell ends.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 1d8.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The target is dealt the damage for two additional attacks that hit it before this spell ends.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Turn","concentration":false,"flavor":"Threads pulling threads pulling threads pulling...","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 1d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The target is dealt the damage for two additional attacks that hit it before this spell ends.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"1d8","damageType":"force","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":97000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"HjcrrWwxPUou0c9o","name":"Echoing Blast","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/sonic/explosion-shock-sound-wave.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures and objects in a 15 foot radius sphere originating from a target location within range to make a basic **Fortitude** saving throw to resist an initial **2d10 bludgeoning damage**. At the start of your next turn, you deal **2d8 bludgeoning damage** to all creatures and objects in the area.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's initial damage roll increases by 1d10 and its delayed damage roll increases by 1d8.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell's damage ignores DBs.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The radius of this spell's area becomes 25 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You conjure a circulation of deadly sound waves.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's initial damage roll increases by 1d10 and its delayed damage roll increases by 1d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"This spell's damage ignores DBs.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The radius of this spell's area becomes 25 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d10","damageType":"bludgeoning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":111000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ID1RhRsZM1xkuplT","name":"Mantle of Hyperreality","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/circle-ouroboros.webp","system":{"description":"When you cast this spell and as a free action at the start of each of your subsequent turns until this spell ends, you cause up to three target creatures within range to make a **Quick-Wits** saving throw. On a failure, it suffers one of the following effects of your choosing (these effects may be selected individually for each target):\n\n* **Minimize.** The target shrinks to size Tiny and cannot inflict damage until the end of their next turn.\n\n* **Reverse Gravity.** Gravity is reversed for the target and they begin falling upwards until the end of its next turn. As a reminder, if unobstructed, a creature would fall upward 500 feet per round.\n\n* **Rewind.** The target is teleported to the space of either where they were one minute ago or when combat began and is disoriented until the end of its next turn. If that space is occupied, they are teleported to the nearest unoccupied space.","levelLabel":"6th Circle","spellLevel":7,"heightenedCircle":7,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"For a world of broken rules and unraveled ambition, you wear it well.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Quick-Wits","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":215000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"IHN7HDOTkWhjTzcv","name":"Siphon Sign","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/life/ankh-shadow-green.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a target creature within range. Until this spell ends, whenever the designated creature is hit with an attack, the attacker **regains 6 ST.**\n\n**Contagion.** As a reaction when a creature affected by a spell effect with contagion trait dies, is knocked out, or burns a Resolve, you may cause a different target creature within range to become affected by the spell.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery per hit increases by 3\\.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"The mark of famine, inverted.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery per hit increases by 3\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":130000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"IMaLozUudOjb8rip","name":"Levitate","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-energy-hold-levitate-blue-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures and objects in a 10 foot radius sphere originating from a target location within range to make a **Poise** saving throw. Subjects of size Large gain advantage on this saving throw, and subjects of size Huge or larger automatically succeed. On a failure, a subject is suspended 10 feet away from the surface nearest to it and ceases to be affected by gravity until this spell ends.\n\nAn affected subject is weightless and may only travel by their own volition when a solid surface is within their Reach. If they kick off of a surface, they may attain a velocity equal to half their Speed traveling in a straight line every round.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The radius of the area increases by 5 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"10 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You unshackle the constraints of gravity.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Poise","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The radius of the area increases by 5 feet.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":123000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"IWAvTqYt89gvds6i","name":"Parley","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/holy/yin-yang-balance-symbol.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 30 foot radius, 30 foot tall cylinder originating from a target floor within range. Until this spell ends, creatures in the area are pacified.\n\n**Permanence.** When this spell begins, you may expend a Resource to cause this spell's duration to become Indefinite.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** Creatures of your choosing in the area are also charmed by you.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** While in the area, you gain advantage on WIS effort and trade checks.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The area is doubled in all dimensions. If you are using this spell's **Permanence** spell trait, this enhancement instead quadruples the total area in all dimensions.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 minute","range":"Reach","shape":"cylinder","shapeSize":"30 feet","duration":"Until your next short or long rest","concentration":false,"flavor":"Let our words stand in the place of spears and our battles be waged in the throes of negotiation. Blood shall not be spilled upon these sacred grounds.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"Creatures of your choosing in the area are also charmed by you.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"While in the area, you gain advantage on WIS effort and trade checks.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The area is doubled in all dimensions. If you are using this spell's **Permanence** spell trait, this enhancement instead quadruples the total area in all dimensions.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":183000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ImOE0OCm9xY9ZBgf","name":"Kindling Light","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/beam-rays-yellow-blue-large.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 20 foot diameter, 120 foot tall cylinder originating from a target floor within range. All creatures in the area **regain 1d8 \\+ 2 ST**. Additionally, an affected creature may take an action once before this spell ends to **regain 1d8 \\+ 2 ST** again.\n\nWhenever a creature regains ST from this spell, they are cleansed of the slowed condition.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** Both of this spell's ST recovery roll increase by 1d8 \\+ 2\\.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** You may choose any number of creatures in this spell's area to be unaffected.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"cylinder","shapeSize":"20 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"Shed the shadow of death.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"Both of this spell's ST recovery roll increase by 1d8 \\+ 2\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"You may choose any number of creatures in this spell's area to be unaffected.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":68000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"JLagy6zhKDxoPylY","name":"Enkindled Filigree","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/explosion-star-glow-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a basic **Courage** saving throw to resist **8d6 radiant damage**. On a failure, an affected creature incurs the following:\n\n* **Incandescent.** At the start of each of its turns, you deal **4d6 radiant damage** to them.\n\n* **Outstanding.** They cannot benefit from being invisible and all other creatures within 15 feet of them are frightened of them until they are further away.\n\n* **Shed Expectations.** When they have 0 ST, they may take an action to end this spell for themself.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's initial damage roll increases by 2d6 and its **Incandescent** damage roll increases by 1d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** Using **Shed Expectations** requires taking two actions instead of one.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The radius of **Outstanding** becomes 30 feet.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"Searing, liquid light paints over a foe with bespeckled embroidery and impossible beauty. Who would dare approach such an icon of fashion?","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Courage","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's initial damage roll increases by 2d6 and its **Incandescent** damage roll increases by 1d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"Using **Shed Expectations** requires taking two actions instead of one.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The radius of **Outstanding** becomes 30 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"8d6","damageType":"radiant","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":176000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Jboewp9rUuTPhSel","name":"Collapsing Vortex","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/air/wind-vortex-swirl-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures and objects in a 30 foot radius sphere originating from a target location within range to make a basic **Poise** saving throw to resist **6d8 force damage**. On a failure, an affected creature is pulled to the center of the area as closely as possible. For the purposes of determining the order of movement, creatures nearer to the center are affected before creatures farther from the center.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The radius of this spell's area becomes 45 feet.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"30 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"The original spellbook's footnote read: \"Do Not Create The Collapsing Vortex\".","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Poise","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The radius of this spell's area becomes 45 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"6d8","damageType":"force","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":147000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Jqv8YO43rKI7YqO3","name":"Overclock","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/movement/trail-streak-zigzag-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"You cleanse the slowed condition from a target creature within range. Additionally, the target's Speed is increased by 5 feet until this spell ends.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"1 Turn","concentration":false,"flavor":"Grease the wheels and watch as the seconds tick by 10% faster.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":18000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"JwyVsss2H5DoS51X","name":"Sanguine Sliver","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/unholy/projectile-spear-glow-pink.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a basic **Fortitude** saving throw to resist **3d6 piercing damage**. On a failure, you may cause a different target creature within range to **regain ST** equal to the amount of damage taken from this spell.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 3d6.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You throw a coiled spike that channels out life forces from its mark.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 3d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"3d6","damageType":"piercing","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":83000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"K8jU1SPt2oGSGYuv","name":"Starfire Cluster","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/explosion-star-large-blue-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"You create three *stars* and distribute them amongst yourself and allied creatures within 15 feet of you. Until this spell ends, a creature with a star may take an action to expend it, add 10 feet to their movement pool, and cause a creature or object they target within this spell's range of them to make a basic **Quick-Wits** saving throw (using your Spell Save DC) to resist **2d8 radiant damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** You may distribute the stars to allied creatures within 30 feet of you.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You create an additional star.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"You initiate a wondrous dance of dazzling starfire.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Quick-Wits","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"You may distribute the stars to allied creatures within 30 feet of you.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You create an additional star.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d8","damageType":"radiant","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":90000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"KI6gAE7sUGxXgj0p","name":"Disintegrate","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-explode-disintegrate.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature or object within range to make a basic **Fortitude** saving throw to resist **30d8 force damage**. For every Resolve the target has remaining, decrease the damage roll by **2d8 force damage**. If the damage from this spell causes the target to expend a Resolve, the remaining damage is not discarded and instead continues to be dealt to the target after it regains the HP and ST from expending the Resolve.\n\nIf this spell kills the target, it is reduced to ash.","levelLabel":"6th Circle","spellLevel":7,"heightenedCircle":7,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Die.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"30d8","damageType":"force","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":210000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"KPek3qEsrbUEZXe5","name":"Round Robin","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-large-white.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target ally within range to **regain 3d4 \\+ 3 ST** and gain advantage on the next attack they make before this spell ends. If they make an attack before this spell ends, they may choose an ally they target within this spell's range of them that has yet to be affected by this spell to gain all of the benefits of this spell.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d4 \\+ 1\\.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"Pay it forward.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d4 \\+ 1\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":167000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"KTadObZrd2aZh31c","name":"Storm Stride","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-strike-sparks-blue.webp","system":{"description":"Until this spell ends, you gain the following benefits:\n\n* **Current.** Once per turn, your first attack that hits after moving in the same turn deals an additional **2d4 lightning damage** to the target of the attack.\n\n* **Flow.** Your Speed is doubled.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 1d4.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Self","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"Gusts and tempest collect beneath your feet \\- thunder and lightning with every footfall.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 1d4.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d4","damageType":"lightning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":136000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"KWiAHWijAWNU8nef","name":"Dawn","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/air/weather-clouds-sunlight.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures and objects within a 30 foot radius, 60 foot tall cylinder originating from a target surface within range to make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **6d6 radiant damage**. Additionally, the area is considered to be filled with sunlight until this spell ends.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"cylinder","shapeSize":"30 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"Vampires hate this one spell\\!","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"6d6","damageType":"radiant","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":149000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"KmBnXiGqPcmAccSi","name":"Briar Plate","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/nature/leaf-armor-scale-green.webp","system":{"description":"Until this spell ends, you gain the following benefits:\n\n* **Armor.** You may act as if you are wearing Stock Armor and without needing to meet its STR requirement.\n\n* **Thorns.** When a melee attack is made against you, you may take a reaction to deal **1d6 piercing damage** to the attacker.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 1d6.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 Minute","range":"Self","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Until the end of your next long rest","concentration":false,"flavor":"Twigs and thorns twist into a spiny carapace.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 1d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"1d6","damageType":"piercing","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":42000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LGev5n6HHmbOCfFs","name":"Witty Retort","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/mouth-smile-deception-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You may cast this spell as a reaction when a target within range hits you with an attack. The target must make a basic **Quick-Wits** saving throw to resist **4d6 psychic damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 4d6.\n\n# **List of 2nd Circle Spells**","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 reaction","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You may win the fight, but I will win the argument.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Quick-Wits","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 4d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"4d6","damageType":"psychic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":101000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LbHJ8wxWDYbGMPAZ","name":"Tricksleeve","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/movement/portal-vortex-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target unattended object of size Tiny within range to be sent away into an extradimensional space of your own. You may end this spell as part of the Retrieve object interaction to retrieve the object. Otherwise, it falls to the ground to an unoccupied space nearest to you if this spell ends through any other means.\n\nIf you cast **Tricksleeve** as a prepared spell, the effect ends early when you cease to have **Tricksleeve** prepared.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 object interaction","range":"Reach","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Until you cast this spell again","concentration":false,"flavor":"With the flick of your wrist, a veil of twilight envelops a small trinket and sequesters it away.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":31000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LiUWqpnMfT4aeD1W","name":"Flit","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/movement/trail-streak-zigzag-teal.webp","system":{"description":"You designate up to three target creatures within range and add 10 feet to their Speed until this spell ends. If an affected creature ends their turn having not moved since the start of their turn, this spell ends early for them.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above, Repeatable)** This spell grants an additional 5 feet to the Speed of all affected creatures.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"You create a fleeting moment of rapid movement.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell grants an additional 5 feet to the Speed of all affected creatures.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":61000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LuioQYjM834NXNfj","name":"Freeze","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/heart-ice-freeze.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a **Fortitude** saving throw. On a failure, a target is frozen until this spell ends. At the end of an affected creature's turn, they may retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success.\n\n**Contagion.** As a reaction when a creature affected by a spell effect with contagion trait dies, is knocked out, or burns a Resolve, you may cause a different target creature within range to become affected by the spell as if it had failed the saving throw.\n\n***Heightening.*** When cast at 6th Circle, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell's saving throw DC is increased by 2\\.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","levelLabel":"5th Circle","spellLevel":6,"heightenedCircle":6,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You stall the biology of a target with a terrifying coldness.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's saving throw DC is increased by 2\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":198000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LzxghB52qHqjyZz8","name":"Augury","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/perception/orb-crystal-ball-scrying-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You ask a question that does not elicit a binary response (i.e. \"yes\" or \"no\" questions are disallowed) and receive an objectively true one-word response, if one exists. You may cast this spell at most once per hour.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** All responses from this spell become full sentences, but each contains both a truth and a lie.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** After receiving the response to the first question, you may ask a second followup question and receive an objectively true one-word response, if one exists.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 minute","range":"None","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"A reading of stars dancing in the palm of your hand.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"All responses from this spell become full sentences, but each contains both a truth and a lie.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"After receiving the response to the first question, you may ask a second followup question and receive an objectively true one-word response, if one exists.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":36000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"M3PBIcbFRj1KKXjW","name":"Fortify","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/defensive/armor-shield-barrier-steel.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a target object within range with a Toughness of 20 or less. Until this spell ends, the target's Toughness is increased by 10\\.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"Fluorescent adhesives suffuse through the material and bind it together.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":63000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"M8Hy6r88yhJ1wwag","name":"Skittering Saboteur","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/acid/projectiles-trio-salvo.webp","system":{"description":"You conjure a *skittering saboteur* at a target unoccupied within range that persists until this spell ends. The skittering saboteur is a Tiny object with 15 HP, 18 AC, 0 Toughness, advanced Climbing mobility, and a Speed of 30 feet. This spell ends early if it is destroyed.\n\n**Automaton.** You may issue the *commands* listed below to an object of your choice created by this spell by taking its listed kind of action. Each command may only be performed once per round:\n\n* **Detonate (reaction at any point).** You destroy the skittering saboteur and cause all subjects within 15 feet of it to make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **4d8 acid damage**.\n\n* **Move (free action during your turn).** The skittering saboteur travels up to its Speed.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** The skittering saboteur's HP increases by 15, its AC increases by 1, and this spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"So light, you can barely feel it creep up your shoulder.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The skittering saboteur's HP increases by 15, its AC increases by 1, and this spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"4d8","damageType":"acid","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":131000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"MQFEAgmatdrNqOK1","name":"Glamour","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/mouth-smile-deception-purple.webp","system":{"description":"Before you make a CHA effort or trade check before this spell ends, you may end this spell to gain advantage on the check.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 minute","range":"None","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"You chisel your features to an unbelievable degree of beauty.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":9000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"MSUqd9GnZ0HQmteA","name":"Astral Ballista","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/beam-horizon-strike-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"You conjure an *astral ballista* at a target unoccupied space within range that persists until this spell ends. The astral ballista is a Large object with 60 HP, 15 AC, and 20 Toughness. This spell ends early if it is destroyed. \n\n**Automaton.** You may issue the *commands* listed below to an object of your choice created by this spell by taking its listed kind of action. Each command may only be performed once per round:\n\n* **Dazzlefire Beam (action).** You designate a 15 foot wide line whose length is the range of this spell originating in front of the astral ballista. All creatures and unattended objects in the area must make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **4d10 fire damage**. On a failure, an affected subject is set ablaze with the **Unready** condition trait, imposing disadvantage on **Poise** and **Reflex** saving throws.\n\n* **Force Blast (action).** You designate a 10 foot radius sphere originating from a target location within range of the astral ballista. All creatures and unattended objects in the area must make a basic **Poise** saving throw to resist **4d8 force damage**. On a failure, an affected subject is pushed 10 feet away from the astral ballista and falls prone.\n\n* **Delegate (action).** You designate a target creature within range. Until this spell ends, they may use this spell's **Automaton** trait if the astral ballista is within their Reach (each command may still only be performed once per round between all eligible issuers).\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** The **Dazzlefire Beam** damage roll increases by 1d10 and the **Force Blast** damage roll increases by 1d8.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell's range becomes 120 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The astral ballista's HP increases by 15 and its Toughness increases by 5\\.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"line","shapeSize":"60 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"Twinkling motes of light descend from the sky and coalesce into a massive brass instrument of arcane warfare.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The **Dazzlefire Beam** damage roll increases by 1d10 and the **Force Blast** damage roll increases by 1d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"This spell's range becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The astral ballista's HP increases by 15 and its Toughness increases by 5\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"4d10","damageType":"fire","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":172000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"MipKHlVZQpt0vTtn","name":"Soul Sink","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/death/skeleton-skull-soul-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a target creature within range and cause all other creatures and objects within a 15 foot radius sphere originating from the target to make a basic **Will** saving throw to resist **6d6 necrotic damage**. The target of this spell regains **6 ST** for each creature damaged by this spell.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6 and the target of this spell regains an additional 2 ST for each creature damaged by this spell.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The radius of this spell's area becomes 30 feet.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"The flow of life and death is struck apart, and it flows freely.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Will","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6 and the target of this spell regains an additional 2 ST for each creature damaged by this spell.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The radius of this spell's area becomes 30 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"6d6","damageType":"necrotic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":168000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"MmhSQzud8j9wxkTr","name":"Shard of Memory","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/perception/orb-crystal-ball-scrying-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You create a *shard of memory*, preserving everything you can **perceive** in your immediate surroundings in a Tiny object with 5 HP, 15 AC, and 5 Toughness that persists until this spell ends. The contents of the shard of memory may be an instantaneous moment or up to 6 seconds of experiences. This spell ends early if it is destroyed.\n\nAs an action while holding a shard of memory, a creature may **perceive** the contents of the shard as if they were at the time and place the shard of memory was created.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"None","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Indefinite","concentration":false,"flavor":"A crystallization of a memory, forever stable and unchanging.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":85000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"NaK0SDHeS8s356Gk","name":"Soulburst","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/explosion-fireball-large-red-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You deal **1d6 fire damage** to yourself and cause all other creatures and objects in a 20 foot radius sphere originating from you to make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **2d10 fire damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's self damage roll increases by 1d6 and the area damage roll increases by 2d10.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The radius of this spell's area increases to 30 feet.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"None","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"20 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Your soul erupts in a conflagration of wishful flame.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's self damage roll increases by 1d6 and the area damage roll increases by 2d10.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The radius of this spell's area increases to 30 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d10","damageType":"fire","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":89000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"O0uiW6JWrUBan0TU","name":"Nebulaic Barrage","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/projectiles-salvo-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You roll Xd10, where X is your spellcasting modifier, and fire a number of missiles equal to the total. You may direct each missile to strike one target creature and multiple missiles may be directed against one creature. A creature is dealt **1d6 force damage** for each missile that strikes them. If multiple missiles strike one target, the missiles are collectively considered to be one instance of damage.","levelLabel":"6th Circle","spellLevel":7,"heightenedCircle":7,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"120 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You recreate the chaotic birth of stars as a shower of arcane missiles.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"1d6","damageType":"force","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":217000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OFusHs97zbQ1fHqI","name":"Locumance","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/movement/trail-streak-zigzag-teal.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a basic **Poise** saving throw to resist **20d6 force damage**. On a failure, an affected creature is forcibly teleported to a target unoccupied space within range.\n\n***Heightening.*** When cast at 6th Circle, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll becomes 24d6.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","levelLabel":"5th Circle","spellLevel":6,"heightenedCircle":6,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"The art of making you both the pen and the paper.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Poise","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll becomes 24d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"20d6","damageType":"force","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":200000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OJdaTale3NeeToPb","name":"Reticence Sigil","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-green-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You grant a target creature within range the following effects until this spell ends:\n\n* **Anti-Scry.** They are invisible to creatures perceiving using the **Scrying** spell trait.\n\n* **Anti-Sensor.** The **Sensor** spell trait does not activate for them.\n\n* **Anti-Telepathy.** Telepathic communications with them fail.\n\n* **Thought Guard.** They gain advantage on **Will** saving throws.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 minute","range":"Reach","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Until the end of your next long rest","concentration":false,"flavor":"A spiraling glyph shaped to channel informative energies into itself and then safely disperse it.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":185000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"OZvktW0VwzOmwXgI","name":"Radiant Arsenal","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/swords-light-glowing-white.webp","system":{"description":"You designate up to three target allies within range. Until this spell ends, whenever an affected creature hits with a weapon attack, they deal an additional **1d8 radiant damage**. If a d8 rolled for this spell's damage has an outcome of 8, this spell is *upgraded* for all affected creatures until this spell ends.\n\nWhile this spell is upgraded, the additional damage of this spell increases to **1d10 radiant damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Costs 2 Selections)** This spell's normal damage die increases to 2d8 and the upgraded damage die increases to 2d10.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"Tempered souls forge their own fate.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"**(Costs 2 Selections)** This spell's normal damage die increases to 2d8 and the upgraded damage die increases to 2d10.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"You target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"1d8","damageType":"radiant","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":165000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"P6yMRysRRQsMtAKp","name":"Bitter Finality","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/heart-ice-freeze.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target within range to become slowed until this spell ends. This spell ends early if you are ever further than this spell's range from the harrowed target.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make a weapon attack. If the attack hits a target slowed by this spell, it deals an additional **6d8 cold damage** to the target.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 3d8.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** If a target is dealt **cold damage** by this spell, it becomes stuck until either the end of its next turn or when this spell ends.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell increases to 60 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You know how it all ends. The long draw to emptiness. A future devoid of warmth.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 3d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"If a target is dealt **cold damage** by this spell, it becomes stuck until either the end of its next turn or when this spell ends.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell increases to 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"6d8","damageType":"cold","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":103000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"PB7eOdwxOZ9StEH6","name":"Squall","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/air/wind-tornado-wall-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures and objects within a 25 foot cube centered in front of you to make a basic **Poise** saving throw to resist **6d6 bludgeoning damage.** On a failure, an affected creature or object is pushed 30 feet away from you and falls prone.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** On a failure, an affected creature or object is pushed 60 feet away from you rather than 30 feet.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"None","shape":"cube","shapeSize":"25 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Thunder crackles in the distance as you echo the wrath of the sky.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Poise","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"On a failure, an affected creature or object is pushed 60 feet away from you rather than 30 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"6d6","damageType":"bludgeoning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":169000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"PTAbAghKc8bcv0CA","name":"Wild Briars","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/nature/root-vines-entwined-leaves.webp","system":{"description":"You create a *thicket* represented as a 15 foot radius sphere originating from a target location within range that persists until this spell ends. All creatures in the thicket must make a **Poise** saving throw. On a failure, an affected creature is restrained until this spell ends. Once per round, a creature restrained by this spell may take an action to retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success.\n\nWhile this spell persists, the surface spaces in the thicket are considered to be difficult terrain, and at the start of each of your turns, you may take a free action to choose one of the following to occur:\n\n* **Entangle.** You cause all creatures in the thicket to make a **Poise** saving throw. On a failure, they are restrained by this spell.\n\n* **Spread.** The radius of the thicket increases by 10 feet, to a maximum radius of 100 feet.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above, Repeatable)** When you cast this spell, you may designate a target allied creature and make them immune to the effect of this instance of this spell.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.\n\n# **List of 4th Circle Spells**","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You conjure a ravenous briar patch that continually consumes the earth.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Poise","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"When you cast this spell, you may designate a target allied creature and make them immune to the effect of this instance of this spell.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":171000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"PkDbmxwey7IDGoaf","name":"Receive Spirit","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/death/grave-tombstone-glow-teal.webp","system":{"description":"You call forth the soul of a dead creature from a target *vestige* within range that belongs to it. The vestige may be a full or partial corpse or skeleton, but must have its skull at the minimum.\n\nUntil this spell ends, you may ask the soul up to three questions and it is compelled to answer each of them. The soul is only able to answer your questions using the knowledge it had up to the moment of its death, though it may recognize you and choose to answer your questions differently based on your identity, and it may try to deceive you.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** The soul's answers must be truthful, though they may be incomplete.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The target vestige no longer requires a skull and may now instead be an object owned by the soul during its life.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** You may ask up to five questions instead of three.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 minute","range":"Reach","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"You follow the threads tethered to their remains and close possessions, drawing their soul from endless sleep and beseeching it for its knowledge.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The soul's answers must be truthful, though they may be incomplete.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The target vestige no longer requires a skull and may now instead be an object owned by the soul during its life.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You may ask up to five questions instead of three.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":184000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"PlwFxMmWBvpzkCwh","name":"Frostwave","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/wave-water-rolling-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures and objects in a cone in front of you whose length is the range of this spell to make a basic **Fortitude** save to resist **9d6 cold damage**. Additionally, all creatures in the area are slowed until this spell ends.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 3d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell's damage ignores DBs.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"cone","shapeSize":"30 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"You send out a rolling fog of frigid doom.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 3d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"This spell's damage ignores DBs.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"9d6","damageType":"cold","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":156000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Q9z2GtbSO7HLXGmB","name":"Lucent Flare","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/projectile-flare-expliosion-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"You create a 15 foot radius sphere originating from a location within range you are at least aware of (even through obstructions). All creatures and objects must make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **2d6 radiant damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The radius of this spell's area becomes 30 feet.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You produce a glimmer of an undeniable, irradiant truth.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The radius of this spell's area becomes 30 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d6","damageType":"radiant","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":72000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QGuKHdBuNWfsMNY5","name":"Fissile Runes","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-red-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You make a weapon attack.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may use an additional action when this spell begins to make another weapon attack.\n\nBoth attacks have the following effects:\n\n* **If it hits,** you bestow 1d4 of *volatile dice* onto the target.\n\nAt the end of the current turn, any creature that has volatile dice explodes and deals **force damage** to all creatures and objects within 5 feet of them equal to the total of their volatile dice. Afterwards, all volatile dice are discarded.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** When an attack hits, you bestow an additional 1d4 volatile die onto the target.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The volatile dice explode in a 15 foot radius.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"None","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You've learned to trace a fuse onto the weave itself.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"When an attack hits, you bestow an additional 1d4 volatile die onto the target.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The volatile dice explode in a 15 foot radius.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"volatile dice total","damageType":"force","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":60000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QLINPHTPWkKhWhMh","name":"Dance Fever","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/mask-yellow-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You cause up to three target creatures within range to make a **Will** saving throw. On a failure, a creature is charmed by you until this spell ends. While charmed by this spell, an affected creature is stunned as they dance in place. At the end of an affected creature's turn, they may retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success.\n\nOnce per round until this spell ends (including when you cast this spell) you may take an action to add half your Speed to your movement pool and cause an additional creature within range to make a **Will** saving throw. On a failure, the target becomes charmed by this spell in the same manner as above.\n\nWhen you spend movement granted by this spell, all creatures you have charmed by this spell travelare forcibly moved in the same direction and distance as your movements.\n\n***Heightening.*** When cast at 6th Circle, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** The DC of all saving throws imposed by this spell are increased by 2\\.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** this spell's range becomes 120 feet.","levelLabel":"5th Circle","spellLevel":6,"heightenedCircle":6,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"Your infectious energy causes others to join you in a big dance.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Will","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The DC of all saving throws imposed by this spell are increased by 2\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"this spell's range becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":197000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QPFsaiykEZVvQ0M4","name":"Facsimispell","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/mask-metal-silver-white.webp","system":{"description":"As you cast this spell, you choose an Arcane spell effect, and the casting of this spell appears identical to that of the chosen spell. You create a *facsimile* of the chosen spell. This spell's range and duration is equal to that of the chosen spell. The facsimile has the following properties:\n\n* **Disillusioned.** The spell effect chosen for the facsimile must not already have the **Illusion** trait.\n\n* **Non-Transformitive.** The facsimile cannot cause subjects to become invisible or polymorphed to achieve the appearance of its effect.\n\n* **Unconvincing.** The **Illusion** trait of this spell only applies to creatures that would not be affected by the facsimile's spell effect. Creatures that would be affected by the facsimile's spell effect know it is not real.\n\n* **No Heightening.** The facsimile acts as if it were cast at its baseline Circle.\n\n\n**Illusion.** This spell effect is intangible but creatures perceive it as real until they attempt to physically interact with it. As an action, a creature that **perceives** this effect may make a **Quick-Wits** saving throw. On a success, the effect becomes obviously illusory to them.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"Variable","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"Variable","duration":"Variable","concentration":false,"flavor":"Often, the impression of a spell is all that is necessary.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Quick-Wits","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":59000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"QVTU8lorZggkfAN5","name":"Enervate","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-life-soul-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a **Fortitude** saving throw. On a failure, an affected creature incurs disadvantage on all STR combat and effort checks and halves the damage dealt by all weapon attacks they make while using melee or Thrown fighting styles.\n\nAt the end of an affected creature's turn, they may retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell's saving throw DC is increased by 2\\.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You may target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You impose a withering frailness upon a foe's vigor.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's saving throw DC is increased by 2\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You may target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":113000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Qo48hI4I3Vk4jKLv","name":"Tidal Blessing","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/wave-water-teal.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to **regain 4d6 \\+ 4 ST** and become cleansed of the ablaze condition. Additionally, the target is immune to the ablaze condition until this spell ends.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 4d6 \\+ 4\\.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"A deluge of refreshing sea foam washes away the weight of misery.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 4d6 \\+ 4\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":95000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"R1Oz2eW0pOeKxqXq","name":"Antivenom","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/nature/root-vine-caduceus-healing.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to **regain ST** equal to your spellcasting modifier. Additionally, if the target is poisoned or is incurring potion toxicity penalties, those effects are suppressed until this spell ends.\n\n**Expound.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins. If you do, the ST recovery roll increases by **Xd6**, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"A small dose to stave off the worst effects.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"R9WLhpYXtjyHSL1S","name":"Mischief","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/mask-yellow-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You may choose for the casting of this spell to be imperceptible. You create one of the following effects of your choosing:\n\n* **Flicker.** You cause a target Tiny flammable object within range, such as a torch or candle, to either become ablaze or become cleansed of being ablaze.\n\n* **Lock.** You close and lock a target door, container, or otherwise lockable object within range.\n\n* **Veiled.** You cause a target Tiny object within range to be unnoticeable unless someone is searching for it for the next hour.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"It's the minor bits of chaos that keep them guessing.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":16000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"RORBa7Nnk0x4Z8Yz","name":"Spore Plume","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/nature/mushroom-glow-red.webp","system":{"description":"You create a 15 foot diameter sphere originating from a target location within range filled with an opaque cloud that persists until this spell ends. Creatures other than you are unable to perceive into or out of the area using normal senses. The cloud is an intangible object that does not prevent other subjects from occupying its space and has 5 HP, an AC of 10, 0 Toughness, and immunity to all damage except **bludgeoning damage** dealt in an area. A strong wind may also dissipate the cloud. This spell ends if the cloud is broken.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make a weapon attack. If the attack hits a creature in the cloud, it deals an additional **4d8 poison damage** to the target.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** Your allies are able to perceive into or out of the area using normal senses.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The diameter of this spell's area increases by 10 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"You join the fungal chorus\\!","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"Your allies are able to perceive into or out of the area using normal senses.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The diameter of this spell's area increases by 10 feet.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"4d8","damageType":"poison","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":135000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"RREt1ujuNuOCgd5r","name":"Glacial Grasp","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/barrier-ice-crystal-wall-jagged-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You create a wall made of ice that is 5 feet thick, 10 feet tall, and 15 feet wide whose endpoints are target surfaces within range. The wall may be bent and curved at your choosing, but cannot be formed into a ring. Each 5 foot length section of the wall has 10 HP, an AC of 10, and 5 Toughness. Creatures are incapable of climbing the wall without advanced Climbing mobility. When this spell ends, all sections of the wall are destroyed.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make a weapon attack. If the attack hits a target within 5 feet of the wall, it deals an additional **9d8 cold damage** to the target and the target becomes stuck to the wall until this spell ends. Once per round, an affected creature may take an action to make a **Poise** saving throw, ending the effect on a success.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 3d8.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** If the target fails the **Poise** saving throw, they become restrained until this spell ends.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You form a wall of living ice and attempt to pin a creature to it.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Poise","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 3d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"If the target fails the **Poise** saving throw, they become restrained until this spell ends.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"9d8","damageType":"cold","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":157000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"SI2ORGbwRjo4vl4Y","name":"Maelstrom","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/vortex-water-whirlpool-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You create a *maelstrom* represented as a 20 foot radius, 120 foot tall cylinder originating from a target floor within range that persists until this spell ends. If a creature starts its turn in the maelstrom or moves into it, they must make a **Poise** saving throw. On a failure, an affected creature is restrained by this spell and pulled to the center of the maelstrom. A creature restrained by this spell may take an action to retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success and ejecting themselves out of the maelstrom. If the creature exits the maelstrom while restrained by this spell, they are no longer restrained.\n\nUnattended objects in the maelstrom's path are automatically restrained and pulled to the center of the maelstrom. At the end of every round, creatures and objects restrained by the maelstrom is dealt **10d6 bludgeoning damage**.\n\nAdditionally, once per round, you may take an action to cause the origin point of the maelstrom to travel up to 30 feet to a target floor within range. All creatures and objects already restrained by this spell are moved with the maelstrom. Any creature or object the maelstrom passes over during this movement is subjected to its effects similar to above.\n\n***Heightening.*** When cast at 6th Circle, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* This spell's damage die becomes 12d6.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The radius of this spell's area becomes 40 feet.","levelLabel":"5th Circle","spellLevel":6,"heightenedCircle":6,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"120 feet","shape":"cylinder","shapeSize":"20 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"A tornado forms out of torrential winds and whirling seawater, sweeping up everything in its wake.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Poise","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage die becomes 12d6.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The radius of this spell's area becomes 40 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"10d6","damageType":"bludgeoning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":201000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"SgbbcWGj2SHuy0w3","name":"Inescapable Sight","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/perception/third-eye-blue-red.webp","system":{"description":"You create a 20 foot radius sphere originating from a location within range you are at least aware of (even through obstructions). All creatures and objects must make a basic **Will** saving throw to resist **4d6 psychic damage**. Additionally, you are aware of all subjects in this spell's area until the end of your next turn.\n\n**Expound.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins. If you do, you double the radius of the sphere and negate all of the **psychic damage** this spell would have dealt.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The radius of this spell's area becomes 30 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"20 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Let it be known. Let I be known.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Will","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The radius of this spell's area becomes 30 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"4d6","damageType":"psychic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":121000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Sn0aggo5qyR0Ebo1","name":"Imprisonment","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/encase-creature-humanoid-hold.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target within range to make a **Courage** saving throw. On a failure, they are sent to a harmless demiplane until this spell ends. At the end of an affected creature's turn, they may retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success.\n\nWhen this spell ends, they return to the nearest unoccupied space from where they left.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** While in the harmless demiplane, the target is incapacitated.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You shove a target into a pocket dimension.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Courage","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"While in the harmless demiplane, the target is incapacitated.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":160000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"TCEndPy9ukMn399N","name":"Withering Cull","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/death/hand-withered-gray.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature or object within range to make a basic **Fortitude** saving throw to resist **4d10 necrotic damage**. If the target currently has no Resolve, they incur disadvantage on the saving throw from this spell.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 4d10.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"Reach","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You grab hold of an enemy and call it to its death.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 4d10.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"4d10","damageType":"necrotic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":100000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"TkkdpissVKVoD3Op","name":"Circle of Renewal","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/life/cross-area-circle-green-white.webp","system":{"description":"You designate up to three target creatures within range. As an action once per round until this spell ends, you may cause all targets to **regain 2d6 \\+ 2 ST**. If at the end of any turn during combat all affected creatures are within 5 feet of another affected creature, this spell is *upgraded* for all affected creatures.\n\nWhile this spell is upgraded, an affected creature may ignore effects that prevent them from regaining ST and this spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d6.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d6 \\+ 1\\.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"The bolstering strength of those around you amplifies your recovery.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d6 \\+ 1\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":106000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"TmE9aqAIHEJBVg2S","name":"Chain Lightning","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolts-strike-salvo-blue.webp","system":{"description":"When this spell begins and at the start of your next turn, you may cause up to five target creatures within range where each target is within 10 feet of at least one other target to make a basic **Fortitude** saving throw to resist **5d6 lightning damage**. On a failure, an affected creature either takes one fewer action on their next turn or takes one fewer action when they burn a Resolve, whichever happens first.\n\n***Heightening.*** When cast at 6th Circle, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* This spell's damage roll becomes 6d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** A creature that fails this spell's saving throw is also disoriented until the end of its next turn.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** You may target two additional targets within range.","levelLabel":"5th Circle","spellLevel":6,"heightenedCircle":6,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You feel the shadow of unlimited power as electricity arcs between your fingertips.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll becomes 6d6.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"A creature that fails this spell's saving throw is also disoriented until the end of its next turn.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"You may target two additional targets within range.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"5d6","damageType":"lightning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":195000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ULjJX5f27UjnQk5M","name":"Triple Take","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/time/clock-analog-gray.webp","system":{"description":"You may cast this spell as a reaction at any point. You grant up to two target creatures within range other than yourself an additional reaction that they may take before the start of their next turn. Reactions granted from **Triple Take** cannot be used to cast **Triple Take**.\n\n***Heightening.*** When cast at 6th Circle, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell's casting time is reduced to a free action.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** You target a third creature within range other than yourself.","levelLabel":"5th Circle","spellLevel":6,"heightenedCircle":6,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 reaction","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Seeing what is ahead, you steer the immediate future off its course.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's casting time is reduced to a free action.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You target a third creature within range other than yourself.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":206000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"UWODoPG8OReoUuE9","name":"Fireball","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/explosion-fireball-large-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures and objects in a 20 foot radius sphere originating from a target location within range to make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **4d8 fire damage**.\n\n**Expound.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins. If you do, you cause all creatures that failed the saving throw as well as all objects and unoccupied surface spaces in this spell's area to be set ablaze.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The radius of this spell's area becomes 30 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"20 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"A white hot point of light explodes into destructive flames.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The radius of this spell's area becomes 30 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"4d8","damageType":"fire","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":116000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"UjCg7nQMggFCDTYp","name":"Astral Darts","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/projectile-stars-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You deal **2d6 force damage** to up to three targets within range.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You may target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You sling bolts of energized stardust as a barrage of seeking missiles.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"You may target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d6","damageType":"force","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":39000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"V6ntgTa1qsPrvSCQ","name":"Equivalent Exchange","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/elements-air-earth-fire-water.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a target ally within range. Until this spell ends, whenever the target takes elemental damage, you may take a reaction to convert the elemental damage inflicted to a different elemental damage type of your choosing.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** When you take this spell's reaction, you may convert the inflicted elemental damage to a physical damage type of your choosing.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"Elemental energies cannot be created nor destroyed; they merely change form.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"When you take this spell's reaction, you may convert the inflicted elemental damage to a physical damage type of your choosing.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":114000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"WG7QRBNREWrdwuBm","name":"Heal","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-hand-gold-green.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to heal 1d8 HP.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's healing roll increases by 1d8.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine","primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 Minute","range":"Reach","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Vermillion sparks flicker from the palm of your hand, igniting the process of regrowth.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's healing roll increases by 1d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":65000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"WKHcEX3OphrozYJx","name":"Fog Cloud","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/air/fog-gas-smoke-dense-white.webp","system":{"description":"You create a 15 foot radius sphere originating from a target location within range filled with an opaque smoke that persists until this spell ends. Creatures are unable to perceive into or from the area using normal senses. The area is an intangible object that does not prevent other subjects from occupying its space and has 5 HP, an AC of 10, 0 Toughness, and immunity to all damage except **bludgeoning damage** dealt in an area. A strong wind may also dissipate the smoke. This spell ends if the area is broken.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** You may take an action once per round to move the centerpoint of the area up to 30 feet to a target location.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The radius of the area is increased by 5 feet and the smoke's HP is increased by 5\\.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You envelop an area in an opaque mist.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"You may take an action once per round to move the centerpoint of the area up to 30 feet to a target location.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The radius of the area is increased by 5 feet and the smoke's HP is increased by 5\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":62000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"WYIDxPnrJrRVq9TS","name":"Sign","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/holy/prayer-hands-glowing-yellow-white.webp","system":{"description":"You may choose for the casting of this spell to be imperceptible. You create one of the following effects of your choosing:\n\n* **Light.** You cause a target object within range to illuminate its surroundings for the next hour.\n\n* **Preservation.** You cause a target object within range to cease rotting or spoiling for the next hour. If the target is a corpse, it cannot be raised as undead while affected by this spell.\n\n* **Soulsearch.** You learn the number of creatures that are within 30 feet of you.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Reach","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"With a small miracle, you nudge the world onto a better path.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":22000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"WgGjNM9QZP93qC95","name":"Listener Glyph","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-green.webp","system":{"description":"You create a *listener glyph* at a target unoccupied surface space, a Tiny object with 5 HP, 15 AC, and 5 Toughness until this spell ends. The listener glyph is invisible and stuck onto the target surface.\n\n**Sensor.** This spell trait activates when a certain *trigger* is met, and when this spell begins, you may except any number of creatures from triggering this spell. For this spell, the trigger is a word or phrase you choose when this spell begins, and this spell trait activates when the chosen word or phrase is spoken by a creature within 60 feet of the designated surface. When this trait activates, you are notified this occurred.\n\n**Scrying.** As an action, you may choose an object created by this spell and begin perceiving as if you were located at it. As a free action, you may end this effect. While perceiving in this manner, you are only able to hear.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 minute","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Indefinite","concentration":false,"flavor":"You inscribe a sigil that quickly fades, leaving behind an imperceptible mark through which you may listen in when the time is right.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":71000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"XoyLXzLxeQGDFsZQ","name":"Meteor Swarm","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-meteor-salvo-heavy-red.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures in a 60 foot radius sphere originating from a target location within range to fall prone and be set ablaze. Immediately afterwards, they must make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **6d10 fire damage**. Once per round, including the round you cast this spell, you may take an action to repeat this spell's effect.","levelLabel":"6th Circle","spellLevel":7,"heightenedCircle":7,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"1 mile","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"60 feet","duration":"4 Rounds","concentration":true,"flavor":"For you, doomsday is the day the sky fell and shattered your ramparts. For me, it was Tuesday.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"6d10","damageType":"fire","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":216000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Xu3arG9VUHxn4Z3R","name":"Cindering Oath","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-orange.webp","system":{"description":"Until this spell ends, you gain the following benefits:\n\n* **Conflagration.** When this spell ends, you are set ablaze.\n\n* **Ferocity.** All attack checks you make gain advantage.\n\n* **Flint Strikes.** Whenever you hit a creature or object with an attack twice within a single turn, the target is set ablaze.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** When this spell ends, you may choose to set all surface spaces within 10 feet of you ablaze.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"Self","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"A solemn vow spoken in the tongue of flame: burn bright and burn beautifully.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"When this spell ends, you may choose to set all surface spaces within 10 feet of you ablaze.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":105000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Y0igFLIwKfvZzCuM","name":"Frigid Gauntlet","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/strike-weapon-blade-ice-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You gain DB 5 against **physical damage** until this spell ends.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make a weapon attack. If the attack hits, it deals an additional **3d8 cold damage** to the target.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** The DB gained from this spell increases by 5 and its damage roll increases by 2d8.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** Whenever this spell's DB is broken, you deal **1d8 cold damage** to all creatures and objects within your Reach.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell's duration becomes 10 minutes.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"None","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"Ice forms around your armaments as crystalline plating.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The DB gained from this spell increases by 5 and its damage roll increases by 2d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"Whenever this spell's DB is broken, you deal **1d8 cold damage** to all creatures and objects within your Reach.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"This spell's duration becomes 10 minutes.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"3d8","damageType":"cold","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":64000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"YaAnk09flKWVSAw9","name":"Acid Jetblades","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/acid/projectile-beams-salvo-green.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target within range to make a basic **Fortitude** saving throw to resist **12d8 acid damage**. On a failure, the target's AC is reduced to their Base AC and all incoming attacks have their critical strike threshold reduced by 2 until this spell ends.\n\nIf the target is an object and has Toughness 15 or below, you are able to slice cleanly through it in any fashion of your choosing as if you had automatically succeeded on a Wreck an Object action.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 4d8.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** The maximum object Toughness this spell may break increases to 20\\.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"You sling jetstreams of acid that can cut through solid steel.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 4d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The maximum object Toughness this spell may break increases to 20\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"12d8","damageType":"acid","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":144000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"YmP4wEkiWdzwoN5H","name":"Earthen Affinity","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/defensive/armor-stone-skin.webp","system":{"description":"Until this spell ends, you gain the following benefits:\n\n* **Wall Cling.** You gain advanced Climbing mobility.\n\n* **Stone Skin.** You gain DB 5 against **physical damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above, Repeatable)** Until this spell ends, you additionally gain basic Burrowing mobility. Choosing this enhancement twice grants advanced Burrowing mobility.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** This spell's DB increases by 5\\.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Self","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"Unbroken by tide, quake, and storm, you and the mountain are one and the same.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"Until this spell ends, you additionally gain basic Burrowing mobility. Choosing this enhancement twice grants advanced Burrowing mobility.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"This spell's DB increases by 5\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":110000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZEKq4HTuvGjpCFxr","name":"Spears of Retribution","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/unholy/projectile-spear-glow-pink.webp","system":{"description":"You designate up to three target creatures within range that are either poisoned, frightened, or incapacitated and cleanse those conditions off of the targets. For each creature you cleanse one or more conditions from, you may cause a different unique target within range to make a basic **Fortitude** saving throw to resist **2d6 necrotic damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 1d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** The target(s) chosen to make a saving throw to avoid damage no longer need to be unique. When choosing a target multiple times, they make one basic saving throw to resist a combined damage roll.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell's range becomes 120 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You draw out the vile malice plaguing your party and turn it against your foes.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 1d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The target(s) chosen to make a saving throw to avoid damage no longer need to be unique. When choosing a target multiple times, they make one basic saving throw to resist a combined damage roll.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"This spell's range becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d6","damageType":"necrotic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":133000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZQChbuxizoVQoY17","name":"Rallying Cry","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/control-influence-rally-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You cause any number of creatures of your choosing within range to **regain 1d6 \\+ 1 ST** and cease being prone.\n\n**Expound.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins. If you do, you double the amount of ST regained for all affected creatures.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d6 \\+ 1\\.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The range of this spell becomes 30 feet.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"15 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Get up\\! Get up, damn you\\!","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d6 \\+ 1\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 30 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":80000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZQVUxIvowvqPeR7q","name":"Bane","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/modfiy-luck-fortune-gray.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a **Will** saving throw. On a failure, an affected creature subtracts 1d4 from all ability checks they make until this spell ends. At the end of an affected creature's turn, they may retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success.\n\n**Contagion.** As a reaction when a creature affected by a spell effect with contagion trait dies, is knocked out, or burns a Resolve, you may cause a different target creature within range to become affected by the spell as if it had failed the saving throw.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** The affected creature must take an action to retry the saving throw. This action may only be taken once per round.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You may target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You burden an opponent with the crushing weight of misfortune.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Will","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The affected creature must take an action to retry the saving throw. This action may only be taken once per round.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"You may target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":40000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZcPNb4jCV7ZVzMwD","name":"Slick Ice","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/orb-ice-web.webp","system":{"description":"You create a 20 foot square area originating from a target location within range that persists until this spell ends. The area is considered difficult terrain unless, and on the first time a creature travels into a space covered by the area since the start of the current turn, it must make a **Reflex** saving throw. On a failure, a creature falls prone.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The side length of the square becomes 10 feet.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"square","shapeSize":"20 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You create a slippery field of condensed, frozen dew.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The side length of the square becomes 10 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":86000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZjSZbbdLt6LuyqAy","name":"Touchstone","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/perception/hand-eye-pink.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a target creature within range. Until this spell ends, you are **aware** of an affected creature and its location. This spell ends early if an affected creature is further than 1 mile from you.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Reach","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Until the end of your next short or long rest","concentration":true,"flavor":"A figment of their essence drawn into a memento. Peering into yourself, you find them in your own heart.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":30000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZpyWdZWUqSKEiawv","name":"Snowball","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/projectile-ice-snowball.webp","system":{"description":"You make a ranged spell attack against a target within range. On a hit, the target is dealt **cold damage** equal to your spellcasting modifier. If this attack scores a critical hit, the target falls prone.\n\n**Discharge.** You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the critical hit threshold for this attack is retroactively reduced by 1 and the damage roll increases by **Xd6**, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"120 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You sling a freezing ball of snow. Occasionally, there is a rock inside.","attackType":"ranged spell attack","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"spellcasting modifier","damageType":"cold","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":{"discharge_description":"Discharge. You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the critical hit threshold for this attack is retroactively reduced by 1 and the damage roll increases by Xd6, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","discharge_damage":"Xd6"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":23000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ZwkQwqmWORBaGnRW","name":"Repaint","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/silhouette-hold-change-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You cause either a target Medium or smaller object within range or a 5 foot square originating from a target surface within range to take on a new appearance until this spell ends. This new appearance can include symbols, text, colors, patterns, or multiple of these, but cannot alter the shape of the target. This spell ends early if you cast **Repaint** again.\n\n**Illusion.** This spell effect is intangible but creatures perceive it as real until they attempt to physically interact with it. As an action, a creature that **perceives** this effect may make a **Quick-Wits** saving throw. On a success, the effect becomes obviously illusory to them.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Reach","shape":"square","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Minute","concentration":false,"flavor":"All things could use a dash of color every now and then.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Quick-Wits","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":21000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"aCD2ntPPLVfSmeUa","name":"Lightning Bolt","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/lightning/bolt-beam-strike-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures and objects in a 5 foot wide line whose length is the range of this spell to make a basic **Reflex** saving throw to resist **2d8 lightning damage**. \n\n**Expound.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins. If you do, you may bend the area's line at one point along the line to any angle or direction you choose.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** You bend the area's line at a point along the line to any angle or direction you choose.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"line","shapeSize":"60 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"With fluid motion you channel a bolt of lightning to strike with violent precision.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"You bend the area's line at a point along the line to any angle or direction you choose.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d8","damageType":"lightning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":70000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"aIV1jJTZCP2Udz91","name":"Starlight Solace","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/beam-rays-yellow-blue-large.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 15 foot diameter, 120 foot tall cylinder originating from a target floor within range. All creatures in the area **regain 4d6 \\+ 4 ST** and are cleansed of the incapacitated condition.\n\n**Expound.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins. If you do, you double the amount of ST regained for all affected creatures.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d6 \\+ 1\\.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell also cleanses the stunned condition for all affected creatures.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"cylinder","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You wrest your allies from the iron grip of cruelty.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d6 \\+ 1\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"This spell also cleanses the stunned condition for all affected creatures.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":188000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"aImPEZbsP7fHaNAH","name":"CastigatorРІР‚в„ўs Will","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/control-influence-crown-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"When a target creature within range makes a saving throw, you may cast **Castigator's Will** as a reaction. The target automatically fails the saving throw.\n\n***Heightening.*** When cast at 6th Circle, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** If the triggering effect has a saving throw to end the effect early, the target automatically fails those subsequent saving throws as well.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell's range becomes 60 feet.","levelLabel":"5th Circle","spellLevel":6,"heightenedCircle":6,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 reaction","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Misguided hope is always the last to crumble.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"If the triggering effect has a saving throw to end the effect early, the target automatically fails those subsequent saving throws as well.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"This spell's range becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":194000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"b4hiBJX4HopzKL1c","name":"Warp Cage","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/lightning/barrier-shield-crackling-orb-pink.webp","system":{"description":"Creatures of your choosing within range when this spell is cast must make a **Quick-Wits** saving throw. On a failure, a creature is pulled into a space adjacent to you. At the start of your next turn, all creatures within 5 feet of you are stunned until the end of their next turn.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** this spell's saving throw DC is increased by 2\\.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 30 feet.\n\n# **List of 5th Circle Spells**","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"15 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Your personality is electrostatic...","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Quick-Wits","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"this spell's saving throw DC is increased by 2\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 30 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":193000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bRBXRE48V1epcWin","name":"Conceptual Entangler","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-large-teal.webp","system":{"description":"You conjure a *conceptual entangler* at a target unoccupied space within range that persists until this spell ends. A conceptual entangler is a Tiny object with 75 HP, 21 AC, and 0 Toughness. This spell ends early if it is destroyed. \n\n**Automaton.** You may issue the *commands* listed below to an object of your choice created by this spell. You must take the listed kind of action in each of the following commands to activate this spell trait, and each command may only be performed once per round:\n\n* **Mindlink (free action).** The conceptual entangler *mindlinks* with a creature it targets within 30 feet of it. The creature remains mindlinked with the conceptual entangler while they are within that distance of each other, and multiple creatures may be mindlinked at the same time. A mindlinked creature gains the following benefits:\n\n  * **Compartmentalization.** They gain DB 20 against **psychic damage**.\n\n  * **Complication.** They may ignore **INT** requirements when choosing a heightening enhancement for a heightened spell.\n\n  * **Counterlogic.** They gain advantage on **Quick-Wits** saving throws and are immune to being charmed, disoriented, incapacitated, or stunned.\n\n***Heightening.*** When cast at 6th Circle, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The distance the conceptual entangler may mindlink with creatures becomes up to 60 feet feet away from it. The conceptual entangler gains a Speed of 15 feet and the **Automaton** trait gains the following command:\n\n  * **Move (free action during your turn).** The conceptual entangler travels up to its Speed.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The DB of **Compartmentalization** becomes 30\\.","levelLabel":"5th Circle","spellLevel":6,"heightenedCircle":6,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"A knotted ball of reflective yarn, able to accept and return thought waves directed at it. Not a mirror, but an amplifier of an idea's complexity.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The distance the conceptual entangler may mindlink with creatures becomes up to 60 feet feet away from it. The conceptual entangler gains a Speed of 15 feet and the **Automaton** trait gains the following command:","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"**Move (free action during your turn).** The conceptual entangler travels up to its Speed.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The DB of **Compartmentalization** becomes 30\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":196000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bnzPxDIYYoSWqURi","name":"Shatter","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/sonic/explosion-impact-shock-wave.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures and objects within a 15 foot radius sphere originating from a target location within range to make a basic **Fortitude** saving throw to resist **4d6 bludgeoning damage**. Objects and constructs in the area take double the amount of damage from this spell.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The radius of this spell's area becomes 30 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"All things must crumble before they can be rebuilt.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The radius of this spell's area becomes 30 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"4d6","damageType":"bludgeoning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":129000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"c2S3zRceK2mbSvj2","name":"Death Grip","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/unholy/hand-grasping-green.webp","system":{"description":"You make a ranged spell attack against a target within range. On a hit, the target is dealt **necrotic damage** equal to your spellcasting modifier and is unable to restore HP or ST through means other than burning a Resolve until this spell ends.\n\n**Discharge.** You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, If you do, the damage roll increases by **Xd10**, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"You choke the life out of something before it can renew itself.","attackType":"ranged spell attack","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"spellcasting modifier","damageType":"necrotic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":{"discharge_description":"Discharge. You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, If you do, the damage roll increases by Xd10, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","discharge_damage":"Xd10"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":7000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"c6ZdJlms5Fg3gTKk","name":"Transplanar Crossroads","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/movement/portal-vortex-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You conjure a doorway at a target location within range. The doorway is a Large object with 20 HP, 10 AC, and 30 Toughness. The doorway leads into an extradimensional space and a corresponding doorway inside the space leads back out. Both doorways persist until this spell ends, and this spell ends early if either doorway is destroyed. This spell may not be dismissed early.\n\nAll doorways created from **Transplanar Crossroads** from all casters of the spell lead to the same extradimensional space, though the doorways appear at different locations inside of it. **Transplanar Crossroads** cannot be cast while inside the extradimensional space.\n\nThe GM determines the size, nature, contents, and whether there are other doorways that currently exist inside **Transplanar Crossroad's** extradimensional space.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 minute","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"24 Hours","concentration":false,"flavor":"You unlock a passage into an infamous complex shared by powerful wizards from all corners of the universe. A thin veneer of cooperation buries the endless contingencies and hidden exits sprawling throughout.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":190000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"c7Hvxcv2ToKMDYYH","name":"Razor Claws","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/lightning/claws-unarmed-strike-teal.webp","system":{"description":"This spell may be cast at any point. Until this spell ends, you gain the following benefits:\n\n* **Claws.** When using the Unarmed fighting style, you may convert the damage dealt from your weapon attacks to **slashing** and use your Martial Die to calculate their damage (ignoring the **Minimum Damage** trait).\n\n* **Cling.** If you are falling and a wall is within your Reach when you cast this spell, you stop your fall and negate the falling damage, remaining clung to the wall until you take a free action to let go. When you let go, you leave a foothold where you had dug into the wall.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 reaction","range":"Self","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"Bone, though seemingly immutable, can also be forged like metal.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":20000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"cE5duSyQTQVQ8pGi","name":"Spectral Guardians","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/death/undead-ghosts-trio-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You cause up to three target creatures within range to gain a *spectral guardian* for each creature that immediately causes the creature to **regain 2d6 \\+ 2 ST**. Each creature's spectral guardian lasts until this spell ends and grants the following benefits:\n\n* **Aegis.** Attacks against the creature incur disadvantage.\n\n* **Parting Gift.** After the next time the creature takes damage, they **regain 2d6 \\+ 2 ST**. Afterwards, the spectral guardian dissipates and this spell ends for them.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** Both of this spell's ST recovery roll increase by 1d6 \\+ 1\\.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"Those that answer the call find rest only in duty.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"Both of this spell's ST recovery roll increase by 1d6 \\+ 1\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":187000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dWvUjLthrRnSuCqJ","name":"Parting Gift","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/movement/trail-streak-impact-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You and a willing creature of your choice within your Reach may teleport up to a target unoccupied space within range. Immediately afterwards, you may choose a different target creature or object within 10 feet of your original position to make a basic **Poise** saving throw to resist **8d6 bludgeoning damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 4d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** If the target of this spell's damage fails the saving throw, they are pulled to your original position.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You snap your fingers and make a loud exit.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Poise","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 4d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"If the target of this spell's damage fails the saving throw, they are pulled to your original position.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"8d6","damageType":"bludgeoning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":126000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"daJpyw4HojQ6eymk","name":"Branch Out","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/nature/root-vine-entangled-hands.webp","system":{"description":"You grow two additional *vine arms* that are attached to and usable by your body that persist until this spell ends. While using your vine arms, your Reach is increased by 5 feet. Additionally, whenever you succeed on a Grapple or Pin check using your vine arms, the target of the action takes **2d4 piercing damage**.\n\nWhen this spell ends, your vine arms drop all objects they were holding and release all creatures and objects grappled or restrained by them.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 1d4.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The Reach bonus gained from using your vine arms becomes 10 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You grow an additional vine arm.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Self","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You make like a tree and beat your opponents from afar.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 1d4.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The Reach bonus gained from using your vine arms becomes 10 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You grow an additional vine arm.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d4","damageType":"piercing","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":104000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dl9w2qqU6AMlf41g","name":"Ignition Primer","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/projectile-embers-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You make a ranged spell attack against a target within range. On a hit, the target is dealt **fire damage** equal to your spellcasting modifier.\n\n**Discharge.** You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, you set the target ablaze.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You sling a bolt of sparks and cinders, eager to catch aflame.","attackType":"ranged spell attack","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"spellcasting modifier","damageType":"fire","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":{"discharge_description":"Discharge. You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, you set the target ablaze.","discharge_damage":null}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":12000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"drG7gwiESxIUKfnJ","name":"Translocate","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/movement/portal-vortex-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You teleport to a target unoccupied space within range. Alternatively, you may target a willing creature within range that is your Size and swap places with them.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** You may instead target an unwilling creature within range.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The teleportation does not happen immediately and this spell's duration becomes 10 minutes. When this spell ends (such as by dismissing it), you teleport to the target space or its nearest unoccupied space if occupied.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"3 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"It is speculated that, in reality, memory-transfer and transmogrification are the actual mechanisms.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"You may instead target an unwilling creature within range.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The teleportation does not happen immediately and this spell's duration becomes 10 minutes. When this spell ends (such as by dismissing it), you teleport to the target space or its nearest unoccupied space if occupied.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":140000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"f2mOH14z1YS71gKu","name":"Vengeful Flame","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/flame-burning-hand-white.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to **regain 12d6 \\+ 6 ST**. Additionally, if the affected creature is attacked by an attacker before this spell ends, the attacker is set ablaze and this spell ends.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 4d6 \\+ 4\\.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell's range becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** This spell does not end when it sets an attacker ablaze.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"You summon the will of smoke and ash, of what has been lost and what can be reclaimed.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 4d6 \\+ 4\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"This spell's range becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"This spell does not end when it sets an attacker ablaze.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":170000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"f5z0ovR0uexdcnml","name":"Rime of Reason","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/snowflake-ice-blue-white.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to **regain 20d6 \\+ 20 ST** and become cleansed of the charmed, incapacitated, and stunned conditions. Additionally, an affected creature gains the following benefits until this spell ends:\n\n* They gain DB 15 against **cold** and **fire damage**.\n\n* They gain advantage on **Quick-Wits** and **Will** saving throws.\n\n***Heightening.*** When cast at 6th Circle, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* This spell's ST recovery roll becomes 24d6 \\+ 24\\.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** Additionally, the target is cleansed of the frozen condition.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The DB becomes 25\\.","levelLabel":"5th Circle","spellLevel":6,"heightenedCircle":6,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"The freezing tundra air cuts through to the unyielding truth.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll becomes 24d6 \\+ 24\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"Additionally, the target is cleansed of the frozen condition.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The DB becomes 25\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":203000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"fR1Rkln74PWr1yI0","name":"Glass Hand","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/orb-hand-green.webp","system":{"description":"You conjure a *glass hand* at a target location within range that persists until this spell ends. The glass hand is a Tiny object with 5 HP, 15 AC, 0 Toughness, advanced Hovering mobility, and a Speed equal to this spell's range. This spell ends early if the glass hand is destroyed, if the glass hand is ever further than this spell's range from you, or you cast **Glass Hand** again.\n\n**Automaton.** You may issue the *commands* listed below to an object of your choice created by this spell. You must take the listed kind of action in each of the following commands to activate this spell trait, and each free action command may only be performed once per round:\n\n* **Fetch (action).** The glass hand takes the Pick Up action targeting a Tiny object and then travels up to its Speed towards you.\n\n* **Interact (object interaction).** The glass hand takes the Fidget object interaction.\n\n* **Move (free action during your turn).** The glass hand travels up to its Speed.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"Lightning captured in a hand-shaped bottle. Your fragile accessory is the perfect solution to the problem of unlabeled switches.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":10000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"g0D9w5XhXhZPJFbT","name":"Spike Growth","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/nature/trap-spikes-thorns-green.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 20 foot radius sphere originating from a target surface within range that persists until this spell ends. All surface spaces in the area are considered difficult terrain. For every 5 feet a creature travels through a surface space within this spell's area, you deal **2d4 piercing damage** to them.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 1d4.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** When you cast this spell, you may designate any amount of surface spaces in the area to be excluded from effect of this spell.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The radius of this spell's area becomes 40 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"20 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"A minefield of thorns and spikes covers the land.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 1d4.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"When you cast this spell, you may designate any amount of surface spaces in the area to be excluded from effect of this spell.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The radius of this spell's area becomes 40 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d4","damageType":"piercing","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":134000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"gfxWmxSaG7DtWKwB","name":"Festering Ire","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/death/skull-poison-green.webp","system":{"description":"You make a weapon attack. \n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make another weapon attack. This second attack ignores weapon attack fatigue.\n\nBoth attacks have the following effects:\n\n* **If it hits**, the target is poisoned until this spell ends.\n\n* **If it hits a target that is already poisoned**, the attack deals an additional **3d8 poison damage** to the target and the target is *festering* until this spell ends or they are no longer poisoned. At the start of each of your turns until this spell ends, you deal **3d8 poison damage** to all creatures and objects festering from this spell.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** Both of this spell's damage rolls increase by 1d8.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"None","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"Blades dredged in spells dredged in hate.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"Both of this spell's damage rolls increase by 1d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"3d8","damageType":"poison","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":154000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"gorEvOJubZULyud7","name":"Sleep","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/sleep-bubble-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures in a 15 foot diameter sphere originating from a target location within range to make a **Will** saving throw. A creature gains a degree of advantage on the saving throw for each Resolve they have remaining. Features that alter a creature's susceptibility to being charmed also apply to saving throws imposed by **Sleep**. On a failure, a creature falls prone and unconscious.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The diameter of the area becomes 10 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You close the gap between worlds of the real and those of dreams. It beckons many to cross.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Will","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The diameter of the area becomes 10 feet.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":132000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"hEs7JTPPS6UPI0mA","name":"Void Tentacles","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/unholy/projectile-smoke-tendril-green.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a basic **Courage** saving throw to resist **8d10 cold damage.** On a failure, the creature is restrained by this spell until this spell ends. Once per round, a creature restrained by this may take an action to retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success and taking an additional **8d6 cold damage** on a failure.\n\n**Contagion.** As a reaction when a creature affected by a spell effect with contagion trait dies, is knocked out, or burns a Resolve, you may cause a different target creature within range to become affected by the spell as if it had failed the saving throw. Newly affected creatures are not dealt the initial damage.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's initial damage roll increases by 2d10 and the restrained failure damage roll increases by 2d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell's damage ignores DBs.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You draw horrors from the deepest reaches of the planespace.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Courage","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's initial damage roll increases by 2d10 and the restrained failure damage roll increases by 2d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"This spell's damage ignores DBs.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"You target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"8d10","damageType":"cold","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":192000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"hN16ERMCI6fNKr4d","name":"Shifting Timeline","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/time/clock-spinning-gold-pink.webp","system":{"description":"Choose any number of target willing creatures within range. Those creatures are teleported to target unoccupied spaces within range.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above, Repeatable)** You may additionally target unwilling creatures to be affected if they fail a **Poise** saving throw. If this enhancement is selected twice, there is no saving throw (they are always teleported).\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell's range becomes 60 feet.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Each choice creates an infinite number of parallel timelines. Choose wisely.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"You may additionally target unwilling creatures to be affected if they fail a **Poise** saving throw. If this enhancement is selected twice, there is no saving throw (they are always teleported).","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"This spell's range becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":186000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"idZYmp0aIUnimNlp","name":"Dimensional Anchor","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-chains-shackles-movement-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You conjure a *dimensional anchor* at a target unoccupied space within range and cause all creatures and objects within 15 feet of the dimensional anchor to make a **Poise** saving throw. On a failure, an affected creature or object cannot teleport and cannot move further than 15 feet from the dimensional anchor until this spell ends.\n\nThe dimensional anchor is a Small object that hovers in its place, is immovable, and has 60 HP, 15 AC, and 20 Toughness. This spell ends early if the dimensional anchor is destroyed.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell cannot be dispelled by effects such as **Dispel**.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The dimensional anchor's HP increases by 15 and its Toughness increases by 5\\.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Hour","concentration":false,"flavor":"You weld spacetime into a series of chains anchored in the fabric of space.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Poise","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell cannot be dispelled by effects such as **Dispel**.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The dimensional anchor's HP increases by 15 and its Toughness increases by 5\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":175000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ijyDAcjTftzWagCv","name":"Phantasmal Terror","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/fear-fright-shadow-monster-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature to make a basic **Courage** saving throw to resist **12d8 psychic damage**. On a failure, an affected creature must take a reaction if they have one. If they do, they must travel up to its Speed away from you. Movement caused by this spell does not direct a creature to step into obviously dangerous hazards, such as steep cliffs or pools of acid.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 4d8.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"The specter of fear itself haunts them.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Courage","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 4d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"12d8","damageType":"psychic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":162000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ineii6adVjka0sR2","name":"Telepathic Bond","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-large-white.webp","system":{"description":"You designate any number of target creatures within range. Until this spell ends, any of the affected creatures may telepathically communicate with any other creature affected by this spell that is within 1 mile.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 minute","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Until the end of your next short or long rest","concentration":false,"flavor":"With the bonds we form, we are never too far from another.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":92000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ioTqgEGDaKAxU12j","name":"Pearlescent Cable","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-white.webp","system":{"description":"You conjure a *pearlescent cable*, a 15 foot long cable attached to one or two target surfaces within range that persists until this spell ends. The pearlescent cable is a Small object with 15 HP, 10 AC, and 10 Toughness, and it remains attached to the target surfaces until it is destroyed. This spell ends early if it is destroyed.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Until the end of your next long rest","concentration":false,"flavor":"Raw magic congealed into a glistening chain perfectly suited for joining two things together.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":77000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"j5KtIJHvbzRM63yC","name":"Double Trouble","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/defensive/illusion-evasion-echo-purple.webp","system":{"description":"On the first attack made against you before this spell ends, you may roll a die of a size of your choice. On an even outcome, the attack automatically misses.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make a weapon attack. If the attack hits, it deals an additional **3d8 psychic damage** to the target.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d10.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** You now roll a die on the first two attacks made against you to determine if they automatically miss.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"None","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"You intersperse the real you with an imaginary you as you fight in tandem.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d10.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"You now roll a die on the first two attacks made against you to determine if they automatically miss.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"3d8","damageType":"psychic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":50000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jTsohP1xa5zj0kTa","name":"Warding Circle","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/life/cross-area-circle-green-white.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 15 foot radius, 30 foot tall cylinder originating from a target floor within range and then designate a creature type tag. Until this spell ends, a creature with a creature type tag designated by this spell may not willingly move into the area.\n\n**Permanence.** When this spell begins, you may expend a Resource to cause this spell's duration to become Indefinite.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** Creatures with a creature type tag designated by this spell may now enter the area, but may not willingly move out of the area. This spell's duration becomes 10 minutes.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above, Repeatable)** You may designate an additional creature type tag.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The radius of the area increases by 5 feet. If you are using this spell's **Permanence** spell trait, this enhancement instead doubles each dimension.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 minute","range":"Reach","shape":"cylinder","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"Until the end of your next short or long rest","concentration":false,"flavor":"A ring of salt and hallowed flame marking where the unwanted may not trespass.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"Creatures with a creature type tag designated by this spell may now enter the area, but may not willingly move out of the area. This spell's duration becomes 10 minutes.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"You may designate an additional creature type tag.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The radius of the area increases by 5 feet. If you are using this spell's **Permanence** spell trait, this enhancement instead doubles each dimension.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":98000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jX102sES98zPcqeA","name":"Gelatinous Crew","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/pseudopod-swirl-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You cause any number of willing creatures within range to become polymorphed into a Tier 0 ooze creature form with the following statistics until this spell ends:\n\n* **Movement.** A Speed of 15 feet with advanced Climbing mobility. They are able to squeeze through gaps with diameters of 1 inch or greater.\n\n* **Size.** Size equal to their original form.\n\n* **Modifiers.** STR, DEX, and CON of \\+0, and INT, WIS, and CHA equal to their respective original forms. Their Tier Bonus is equal to their original form.\n\n* **AC.** Their Base AC, Half Guard, and Full Guard AC is 11, 13, and 15, respectively.\n\n* **HP and ST.** They have 50 HP and ST.\n\n* **Coagulate.** As a free action, they may end this spell for them.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 minute","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Until the end of your next long rest","concentration":true,"flavor":"A gross but ultimately harmless liquefaction.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":178000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"jjNGGWapkUz1W5Rd","name":"Theatrics","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/mask-yellow-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You may choose for the casting of this spell to be imperceptible. You create one of the following effects of your choosing:\n\n* **Cue.** You choose a creature you are aware of within range to learn that this spell has been cast on them.\n\n* **Flourish.** You create a harmless sensory effect, such as a puff of smoke, shower of sparks, or spray of confetti at a target location within range that persists until the end of the current turn. The effect can include a visual, auditory, and olfactory component simultaneously.\n\n* **Vibe Check.** You target three or more creatures within range with this spell and learn the surface-level emotion, thought, or idea that is on the majority of the targets's minds.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You exemplify the beauty that arises from the composure of many small things falling into place at just the right time.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":29000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lHM6FNSXljGlnn5G","name":"Deflection Sigil","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-rough-white-teal.webp","system":{"description":"You cause the next critical hit against the target before this spell ends to instead be counted as a normal hit. After this occurs, this spell ends early.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"10 Minutes","range":"Reach","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Until you cast **Deflection Sigil** again or take a long rest","concentration":false,"flavor":"You inscribe a warding tattoo that nudges attacks away from the vital organs.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":8000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lM5iHT8F92fl5cUZ","name":"Toxic Fume","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/air/fog-gas-smoke-green.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures in a 15 foot radius sphere originating from a target location within range to make a **Fortitude** saving throw. On a failure, a creature is poisoned until this spell ends. At the end of an affected creature's turn, they may retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The radius of the area increases by 5 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"15 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"I must have smelt it.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The radius of the area increases by 5 feet.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":139000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"lXmzW36zi5o7M5fX","name":"Fey Crossing","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/nature/root-vine-beanstalk-moon.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 25 foot radius, 50 foot tall cylinder originating from a target floor surface within range. The following effects are created within the area:\n\n* **Looping.** A creature that attempts to travel out of this spell's area instead appears on the diametrically opposite side of the area. This effect does not occur when teleporting or when traveling out of the top or bottom faces of the cylindrical area.\n\n* **Mushrooms.** When you cast this spell, you may plant up to five *mushrooms* each at target 5 foot unoccupied spaces within the area. The mushrooms are invisible to any number of creatures of your choosing. When a creature enters a mushroom's space, the mushroom is destroyed, the creature's movement pool is cleared, and they must make a **Fortitude** saving throw. On a failure, a creature is incapacitated until the end of the current turn.\n\n* **Tree.** A 50 foot tall *tree* appears at the area's centerpoint with a 5 foot diameter trunk. Creatures are pushed out into nearby unoccupied spaces if the tree appears in their space. The top of the tree fans out into a thick canopy covering the top of the cylinder. The canopy is a solid material of 15 Toughness and any holes piercing through it regenerate at the start of your turn.\n\nWhen this spell ends, everything created by this spell instantly disappears.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** When you cast this spell, you may plant three more mushrooms.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"cylinder","shapeSize":"25 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"You overrun an area with fey magic and grow a mighty tree. Its canopy shelters the chaos within.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"When you cast this spell, you may plant three more mushrooms.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":177000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mN93nK1QSwmmVbqn","name":"Dizziness","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/hypnosis-mesmerism-swirl.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a **Quick-Wits** saving throw. On a failure, they are disoriented until this spell ends. At the end of an affected creature's turn, they may retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** The affected creature must take an action to retry the saving throw. This action may only be taken once per round.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You may target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"The floor becomes the ceiling which becomes the floor which becomes the ceiling...","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Quick-Wits","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The affected creature must take an action to retry the saving throw. This action may only be taken once per round.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You may target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":49000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mWloYQnhiZAsNs3l","name":"Hover","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-energy-hold-levitate-teal-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You grant a target creature within range basic Hovering mobility until this spell ends. Additionally, the target immediately adds 20 feet to their movement pool. This movement must be spent hovering.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** You grant advanced Hovering mobility to all affected creatures.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Hour","concentration":true,"flavor":"To outwit gravity, one must simply expose its lies.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"You grant advanced Hovering mobility to all affected creatures.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":159000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"mvzCSoqDm5P86rdn","name":"Counterspell","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-deflect-teal.webp","system":{"description":"Immediately after a target within range casts a spell, but before the spell begins, you may cast **Counterspell** as a reaction. The spell the target just cast is called the *target spell*, and **Counterspell's** effect is determined by the Circle of the target spell:\n\n* **2nd Circle or Below.** If the target spell is less than or equal to 2nd Circle, the target spell ends and produces no effect.\n\n* **Above 2nd Circle.** If the target spell is greater than 2nd Circle, you must make a spellcasting combat check against a DC equal to 10 \\+ (2 x the Circle of the target spell). On a success, the target spell ends and produces no effect.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above, Repeatable)** The maximum target spell Circle where this spell automatically succeeds increases by one.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above, Repeatable)** The range of this spell increases by 30 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 reaction","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"As a spell is being formed, you upset it with an equal but opposite force.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The maximum target spell Circle where this spell automatically succeeds increases by one.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell increases by 30 feet.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":108000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"nJoTFGD8X7EQBJZv","name":"Slippery Form","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/pseudopod-teal.webp","system":{"description":"Until this spell ends, you gain the following benefits:\n\n* **Amphibious.** You are able to breathe underwater.\n\n* **Mobilities.** You gain basic Jumping and Swimming mobility.\n\n* **Slippery.** Grapple checks made against you incur disadvantage.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** Additionally, you gain basic Climbing mobility until this spell ends.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** All mobilities you gain from this spell are advanced.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Self","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Until the end of your next long rest","concentration":false,"flavor":"You channel the adaptability, swiftness, and sliminess of a frog.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"Additionally, you gain basic Climbing mobility until this spell ends.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"All mobilities you gain from this spell are advanced.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":87000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"nMZe6k03u6xTEOOA","name":"Time Stop","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/time/hourglass-yellow-green.webp","system":{"description":"You may only cast this spell on your turn once per round. You take three additional actions of your choosing. Other than your movement, the effects of the actions you take do not occur until all three additional actions are taken.","levelLabel":"6th Circle","spellLevel":7,"heightenedCircle":7,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"Free Action","range":"None","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You unwind the twisting and spiraling continuum of time to splice in a small addition.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":221000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"oXo9HEsYNVDMOBIj","name":"Dusklit Dance","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/beam-strike-orange-gold.webp","system":{"description":"You make a weapon attack. If this attack hits, you may cause a target creature within range to **regain 2d4 ST**.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make another weapon attack. If this attack hits, it deals an additional **2d10 radiant damage** to the target.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 2d4 and its damage roll increases by 2d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** The creature you cause to **regain ST** adds **2d6 radiant damage** to the damage dealt by their next attack that hits within the next 10 minutes.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Draw the line between life and death.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 2d4 and its damage roll increases by 2d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The creature you cause to **regain ST** adds **2d6 radiant damage** to the damage dealt by their next attack that hits within the next 10 minutes.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d10","damageType":"radiant","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":53000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"p2gBmVd3KiGSub80","name":"Defender Drone","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/cog-shield-white-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You summon a *defender drone* at a target unoccupied space within range that persists until this spell ends. The defender drone is a Small object with 15 HP, 15 AC, 10 Toughness, and has a Search DC equal to this spell's Save DC. This spell ends early if it is destroyed, if it is ever further than this spell's range from you, or you cast **Defender Drone** again. The defender drone acts as a sentry outside of combat with its alertness starting as **relaxed**.\n\n**Automaton.** You may issue the *commands* listed below to an object of your choice created by this spell by taking its listed kind of action. Each command may only be performed once per round:\n\n* **Arcane Zap (action).** The defender drone makes a ranged spell attack (using your spell attack bonus) against a target within 30 feet of it. On a hit, you deal **1d10 lightning damage** to the target.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 1d10.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"120 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Until the end of your next long rest","concentration":false,"flavor":"The shrill, blaring noise it makes is sure to awaken even the heaviest of sleepers.","attackType":"ranged spell attack","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 1d10.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"1d10","damageType":"lightning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":46000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pBYEhqCWFrdwlwgc","name":"Thoughtstream","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-spiral-teal.webp","system":{"description":"You target yourself and a creature within range to *connect* both you and them until this spell ends. This spell ends early if any connected creatures are further than this spell's range from each other. All connected creatures gain the following effects:\n\n* **Skim Surface.** They may read the surface thoughts and emotions of any other creature affected by this spell.\n\n* **Dive Deeper.** As a free action, they may cause another creature affected by this spell to make a **Quick-Wits** saving throw (against your Spell Save DC). On a failure, they may learn any deeper thoughts and feelings, including thoughts the creature would want to keep secret. Each connected creature may take this free action for this spell at most once.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"3 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You open your heart and soul to form a channel into another's.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Quick-Wits","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":189000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pLj4LHsTcKSREb7U","name":"Riftwalk","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/movement/portal-vortex-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You teleport to a target unoccupied space within range.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above, Repeatable)** The range of this spell increases by 15 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** You may bring a target willing creature within your Reach with you, teleporting them with you.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"45 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"In a flash, you stride between the trappings of physicality.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The range of this spell increases by 15 feet.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You may bring a target willing creature within your Reach with you, teleporting them with you.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":82000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pfaiEWbnBIBBFV9Q","name":"Expedite Action","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/time/clock-stopwatch-white-blue.webp","system":{"description":"If your initiative partner is targetable and within range, you grant them an additional action they may take before the end of the current turn.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** You instead grant the additional action to a target ally within range.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"With just a word you can put the impossible just within reach.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"You instead grant the additional action to a target ally within range.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":153000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"pvLpfoTJla2iwAAI","name":"Windblast","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/air/air-wave-gust-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You make a ranged spell attack against a target within range. On a hit, the target is dealt **bludgeoning damage** equal to your spellcasting modifier.\n\n**Discharge.** You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the target is pushed 10 feet away from you and the damage roll increases by **Xd6**, where X is half your Tier Bonus.\n\n# **List of 1st Circle Spells**","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You accelerate drifting air currents into a concussive force.","attackType":"ranged spell attack","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"spellcasting modifier","damageType":"bludgeoning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":{"discharge_description":"Discharge. You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the target is pushed 10 feet away from you and the damage roll increases by Xd6, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","discharge_damage":"Xd6"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":32000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"q1TXeGBLv6zhdqBK","name":"Petrify","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/earth/strike-body-stone-crumble.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a **Fortitude** saving throw. On a failure, an affected creature is restrained. While restrained in this manner, an affected creature may take an action to retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success. This action may be taken multiple times within a turn.\n\nIf a creature restrained by this spell ends their turn having not succeeded on a saving throw against this spell, they must expend a Resolve or become turned to stone. If a creature ends their turn having not been turned to stone, this spell ends.\n\nWhile turned to stone, a creature has the following properties:\n\n* They cannot escape this state short of a 7th Circle **Wish** spell.\n\n* They are incapacitated and cease aging.\n\n* They can be treated as an object with an amount of HP equal to its maximum, an AC equal to its Full Guard AC, and 30 Toughness.","levelLabel":"6th Circle","spellLevel":7,"heightenedCircle":7,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Indefinite","concentration":false,"flavor":"You ensnare a target within a statuesque living death.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":218000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qFS8UrhcRiNQUIhP","name":"Animate Interceptor","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/cog-shield-white-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You conjure an *animate interceptor* at a target unoccupied space within range that persists until this spell ends. The animate interceptor is a Small object with 15 HP, 15 AC, 5 Toughness, and advanced Hovering mobility. This spell ends early if it is destroyed.\n\n**Automaton.** You may issue the *commands* listed below to an object of your choice created by this spell by taking its listed kind of action. Each command may only be performed once per round:\n\n* **Project Shield (free action).** You may only issue this command when an ally within 30 feet of the animate interceptor is attacked. The animate interceptor travels to an unoccupied space within 5 feet of the ally and grants them their Full Guard AC against the attack.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above, Repeatable)** The first, third, and fifth times you choose this enhancement, **Project Shield** may be used an additional time per round.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The animate interceptor's HP increases by 10 and its Toughness increases by 5\\.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"While most automata obey the rule of \"do no harm\", some take it a step further.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The first, third, and fifth times you choose this enhancement, **Project Shield** may be used an additional time per round.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The animate interceptor's HP increases by 10 and its Toughness increases by 5\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":35000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qfjWdynDOVcXL936","name":"Missive","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/rune-sigil-hook-white-red.webp","system":{"description":"You compose a message of 30 words or less and choose a creature that you know. You then conjure a note with the message written on it at the chosen creature's location.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 minute","range":"None","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Dear esteemed colleague: I apologize for diverting your attention from your critical studies. Your predilection towards explosive spells yields incredible promise. However, it is absolutely imperative that I tell you-","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":73000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qq4fHIYFX5HFQTrR","name":"Bend Luck","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/buff-luck-fortune-gold.webp","system":{"description":"You designate up to two target creatures within range. Once before this spell ends, an affected creature may choose to do either of the following:\n\n* **Heads.** When an affected creature makes an attack check, they may end this spell for them to gain advantage on the attack check.\n\n* **Tails.** When an affected creature is attacked, they may end this spell for them to impose disadvantage on the attack check.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** An affected creature may each use **Heads** and **Tails** once before this spell ends.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"To flip a coin is to cast yourself amidst the whims of an unthinking universe. It's time to pick a side.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"An affected creature may each use **Heads** and **Tails** once before this spell ends.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":41000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qr6GKdqBoc5Dyp7C","name":"Startle","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/fear-fright-white.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a **Courage** saving throw. On a failure, if the target has no Resolve remaining, they must drop everything they are holding.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Spooked ya\\!","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Courage","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":27000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qrJ3u3SKFwW7Y46J","name":"KeepsakeРІР‚в„ўs Calling","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/perception/orb-eye-scrying.webp","system":{"description":"You learn the name of a target object within range and gain advantage on INT effort or trade checks made to recall information regarding the target object. This spell treats effects with the **Illusion** spell trait as real and determines the name based only on the target's appearance and not its material composition.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"The nature, size, shape, and appearance of an object carries with it a reputation. A name pulled from the threads of artisanship.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":13000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qrKdfeZV7evQBTjA","name":"Violent Bloom","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/nature/plant-sprout-hands-vines.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to **regain 16d6 \\+ 16 ST** and become cleansed of the prone, stuck, and restrained conditions. If the target was stuck or restrained, their next weapon attack that hits before this spell ends *violently blooms* and causes the target of the attack to become stuck until the end of their next turn.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 4d6 \\+ 4\\.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** The weapon attack that violently blooms inflicts restrained instead of stuck.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"Wicked vines untangle your friends and strangle your prey.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 4d6 \\+ 4\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The weapon attack that violently blooms inflicts restrained instead of stuck.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":191000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qsKT6IoEnlua28ZK","name":"Tempest Shield","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/lightning/barrier-shield-orb-pink.webp","system":{"description":"You take a free Raise Shield action. You may also materialize and hold a shield to qualify to take the Raise Shield action, which persists while you gain the benefits of the action. Until this spell ends, whenever a creature or object is within range for the first time since the start of your most recent turn, you may deal **6 lightning damage** to them.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make a weapon attack. If the attack hits, it deals an additional **2d6 lightning damage** to the target.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's area damage roll increases by 3 and its bonus weapon damage roll increases by 1d6.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** When this spell begins, you may travel up to half your Speed immediately. This may be done before using the **Spellstrike** trait.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"10 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"Shimmering storms gather into a protective shield as the planting of your feet resound with rolling thunder.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's area damage roll increases by 3 and its bonus weapon damage roll increases by 1d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"When this spell begins, you may travel up to half your Speed immediately. This may be done before using the **Spellstrike** trait.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"6","damageType":"lightning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":138000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qz9dPOU2v1FRjAwG","name":"Accelerate","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/time/arrows-circling-green.webp","system":{"description":"You allow a target creature within range to take a free Move action.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** On the first and third time this enhancement is chosen, you target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You envision the vast and uncountable possibilities that expand from this very moment. For you, it all falls into place at exactly the right time.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"On the first and third time this enhancement is chosen, you target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":102000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"rXaxBB1uprj5IO2k","name":"Dose of Reality","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/perception/eye-ringed-green.webp","system":{"description":"You grant the following benefits to a target creature within range until this spell ends:\n\n* **No Distractions.** You do not perceive effects with the **Illusion** spell trait as real.\n\n* **Nothing Hidden.** Subjects with the invisible condition or its **Concealed** or **Stealthy** traits do not benefit from them against you.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 minute","range":"Reach","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"Illusory spells are no match for the unimaginative.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":51000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"riU2VSKFvplQ0Owq","name":"Web","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/orb-web-hold.webp","system":{"description":"A 10 foot radius sphere originating from a target surface within range becomes covered in a sticky web until this spell ends. The area is considered difficult terrain, and on the first time a creature or object travels into a space covered by the area since the start of the current turn, it must make a **Poise** saving throw. On a failure, a creature becomes stuck.\n\nA creature stuck by this spell may take an action to retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The radius of the area increases by 5 feet.\n\n# **List of 3rd Circle Spells**","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"10 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You lob a blob of spider silk that explodes into a blast of sticky webs.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Poise","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The radius of the area increases by 5 feet.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":143000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"sBc89eLXUWdIQMBH","name":"Stunning Paradox","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/hypnosis-mesmerism-swirl.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a basic **Quick-Wits** saving throw to resist **24d6 psychic damage**. On a failure, the target is stunned until this spell ends. Additionally, if the target is within the Reach of a creature, that creature may take an action to cause the target to retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success. If an affected creature fails the saving throw when they retry it, the creature that attempted to help them is also stunned until this spell ends.","levelLabel":"6th Circle","spellLevel":7,"heightenedCircle":7,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"You twist a target's thought process into a cascading causal loop.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Quick-Wits","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"24d6","damageType":"psychic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":220000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"sYIRN2I2kngK1uca","name":"Backfire Matrix","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-pentagon-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You cause all creatures and objects within a 20 foot cube originating from a target location within range to make a basic **Fortitude** saving throw to resist **8d8 force damage**. For an affected creature or object that is concentrating on an effect, their concentration ends and this spell's damage roll is replaced with the maximum possible result.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell's damage ignores DBs.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"cube","shapeSize":"20 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"A skilled caster can shield themself from a spell's backfire. An even better one knows how to cause it.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"This spell's damage ignores DBs.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"8d8","damageType":"force","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":173000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"sj39JwEqDMRPSqPA","name":"Acrid Spine","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/nature/trap-spikes-thorns-green.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a 10 foot square area originating on a target surface within range to permanently become difficult terrain and deal **1d4 acid damage** to all creatures and objects on it.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make a weapon attack. If the attack hits, it deals an additional **2d6 acid damage** to the target.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's initial damage roll increases by 1d4 and its bonus attack damage roll increases by 2d6.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The square area's side length becomes 20 feet.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"square","shapeSize":"10 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Caustic spikes rupture the earth as you prepare a deadly blow.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's initial damage roll increases by 1d4 and its bonus attack damage roll increases by 2d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The square area's side length becomes 20 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"1d4","damageType":"acid","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":34000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"sqnjOVomc1zctw9V","name":"SoothsayerРІР‚в„ўs Gaze","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/perception/third-eye-blue-red.webp","system":{"description":"You make a ranged spell attack against a target within range. On a hit, the target is dealt **psychic damage** equal to your spellcasting modifier and you gain advantage on the next Analyze check you make against it before the end of combat.\n\n**Discharge.** You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the damage roll increases by **Xd6**, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","levelLabel":"Cantrip","spellLevel":1,"heightenedCircle":1,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"","shapeSize":"","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"You coalesce the imparted omniscience of gods into a deadly force.","attackType":"ranged spell attack","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"spellcasting modifier","damageType":"psychic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":{"discharge_description":"Discharge. You may take an additional action when you hit with the attack. If you do, the damage roll increases by Xd6, where X is half your Tier Bonus.","discharge_damage":"Xd6"}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":24000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ssrAVjWrI8puBjtC","name":"Lightstream Chaser","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/light/beam-layered-teal.webp","system":{"description":"You make a weapon attack.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make another weapon attack.\n\nBoth attacks have the following effects:\n\n* **Before making the attack,** you teleport to a target unoccupied space within range from which you are able to target a creature with a weapon attack.\n\n* **If it hits,** the attack deals an additional **2d8 radiant damage** to the target.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 1d8.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 30 feet.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"15 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Nestled between the impossible is a slim opportunity which only light is quick enough to reach.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 1d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 30 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"2d8","damageType":"radiant","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":124000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"tA1UXESAgkrPgKvD","name":"Sculpt Earth","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/earth/construct-stone-long-arms.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 60 foot cube originating from a target location within range. All forms of terrain of 10 Toughness or below within the area, such as its floors, walls, and ceilings, may be modified in the following ways:\n\n* **Destruction.** You may destroy floors, walls, or ceilings. You are able to collapse entryways and form new ones.\n\n* **Difficult Terrain.** You may designate any surface in the area to be difficult terrain or be cleared of being difficult terrain.\n\n* **Formation.** You may conjure walls, floors, or ceiling made of a material of 10 Toughness or below.\n\n* **Relocation.** You may take portions of walls, floors, or ceilings and move them to locations within the area.\n\nStructures formed by this spell ignore the effects of gravity while this spell persists. However, once this spell ends, modifications to the terrain made by this spell do not return to their original arrangement. \n\nIf terrain modifications created by this spell would forcibly move a creature or trap them, the creature may make a **Poise** or **Reflex** saving throw. On a success, they may take a reaction to add half their Speed to their movement pool which they may immediately spend as this spell takes effect to find safety.\n\n***Heightening.*** When cast at 6th Circle, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The area's side length becomes 120 feet.","levelLabel":"5th Circle","spellLevel":6,"heightenedCircle":6,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"cube","shapeSize":"60 feet","duration":"1 Hour","concentration":true,"flavor":"You reform the landscape.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Poise or Reflex","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The area's side length becomes 120 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":205000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"tCMcW6Om8gZbML0A","name":"Palefire Scourge","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/unholy/projectile-flame-white-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You deal **1d8 necrotic damage** to a target creature within range. Once per turn until this spell ends, you may deal **1d8 necrotic damage** to an affected creature after they burn a Resolve or when one of their weaknesses activates.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make a weapon attack. If this attack hits an affected creature, it deals an additional **1d8 necrotic damage** to the target.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** Each of this spell's damage rolls increase by 1d8.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** Choose one of the following damage types: **acid**, **fire**, or **force**. All damage dealt by this spell is converted to the chosen damage type.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell's duration becomes 10 minutes but requires concentration.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"A devouring, vacant flame catches hold and singes the soul.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"Each of this spell's damage rolls increase by 1d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"Choose one of the following damage types: **acid**, **fire**, or **force**. All damage dealt by this spell is converted to the chosen damage type.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"This spell's duration becomes 10 minutes but requires concentration.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"1d8","damageType":"necrotic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":76000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"tJGNWPDIgL5nHCyY","name":"Vital Wellspring","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/water/water-well.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to become cleansed of the poisoned condition and gain a *wellspring pool* of 6d8 that persists until either the pool is emptied or this spell ends. At the start of each of the target creature's turns, they may roll their wellspring pool and **regain ST** equal to the total.\n\nIf a die's outcome from the wellspring pool is a 7 or 8, the wellspring pool loses 1d8 on subsequent rollings.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's initial wellspring pool increases by 3d8.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"Reach","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You flood a creature with restorative vigor.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's initial wellspring pool increases by 3d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":142000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"tZ3X8K65j1RtFNCP","name":"Miasma","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/air/fog-gas-smoke-dense-green.webp","system":{"description":"You designate a 20 foot radius, 15 foot tall cylinder originating from a target surface within range that persists until this spell ends. Once per round, if a creature starts its turn in the area or moves into it, they must make a basic **Fortitude** saving throw to resist **8d6 poison damage**. On a failure, an affected creature is poisoned until the start of their next turn.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** Once per round, you may take an action to move the origin of the area up to 30 feet to a target surface within range.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The radius of this spell's area becomes 30 feet.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"cylinder","shapeSize":"20 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"A heavy bog stench wafts out of the ground; so putrid it could kill.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Fortitude","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"Once per round, you may take an action to move the origin of the area up to 30 feet to a target surface within range.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The radius of this spell's area becomes 30 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"8d6","damageType":"poison","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":181000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"thZKWLr4VFZCQZn7","name":"High Five","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-hand-gold-green-light.webp","system":{"description":"You add your Speed to your movement pool. Until this spell ends, you may take a free action to cause a target creature within range that has yet to be affected by this spell to **regain 4d4 \\+ 4 ST**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 2d4 \\+ 2\\.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The movement gained from this spell is doubled.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"Reach","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Turn","concentration":false,"flavor":"An ancient spell, first cast by the realest of them all.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 2d4 \\+ 2\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The movement gained from this spell is doubled.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":119000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"tzUVEhCSwcfNJv0R","name":"Pseudochemical Heart","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/life/heart-cross-strong-flame-purple-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target willing creature within range to gain the following effects until this spell ends:\n\n* **Adrenaline Pool.** An affected creature has an *adrenaline pool* of dice that starts at 0d4. When this spell ends for a creature, they are dealt **injuring poison damage** equal to a rolling of the adrenaline pool.\n\n* **Expand.** Once during an affected creature's turn or when they expend a Resolve, they may immediately take an action of their choice as a free action (which may be used as part of a multiaction). If they do, they add 3d4 to their adrenaline pool.\n\n* **Contract.** As an action, an affected creature may remove 3d4 from their adrenaline pool.\n\n* **Expire.** After an affected creature has used **Expand** or **Contract** a combined total of five times, this spell ends early for them.\n\n***Heightening.*** When cast at 6th Circle, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell ends after using **Expand** or **Contract** a combined total of seven times.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** An affected creature may add half their Speed to their movement pool when they **Contract**.","levelLabel":"5th Circle","spellLevel":6,"heightenedCircle":6,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Reach","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"A rune-laiden, pulsating leather bag crafted with the express purpose of pumping you up.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell ends after using **Expand** or **Contract** a combined total of seven times.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"An affected creature may add half their Speed to their movement pool when they **Contract**.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"adrenaline pool roll","damageType":"poison","injuring":true,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":202000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"uHI3RC6MeU8ifDXq","name":"Fear","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/fear-fright-shadow-monster-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target creature within range to make a **Courage** saving throw. On a failure, a creature is frightened of you until this spell ends. When a creature frightened from this spell starts their turn, they must also choose one of the following penalties to apply to themselves for the turn:\n\n* **Fight.** The creature must take the Attack action against you this turn. The next attack against the creature gains advantage.\n\n* **Flight.** The creature attempts to end its turn further away from you by at least an amount equal to its Speed.\n\n* **Freeze.** The creature is stuck until the end of their turn.\n\nAt the end of an affected creature's turn, they may retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell's saving throw DC is increased by 2\\.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You may target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You don a visage of pure amorphic horror.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Courage","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's saving throw DC is increased by 2\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You may target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":115000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ufsPsyMPnm8yjOp6","name":"Dauntless Pledge","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/holy/prayer-hands-glowing-yellow-white.webp","system":{"description":"You cause any number of creatures of your choosing within range to **regain 3d6 \\+ 3 ST** and become immune to being frightened until this spell ends.\n\n**Expound.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins. If you do, you double the amount of ST regained for all affected creatures.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d6 \\+ 1\\.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell's **Expound** trait cannot be activated and may only target one creature. The amount of ST recovery granted from this spell is doubled.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The range of this spell becomes 30 feet.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"15 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Round","concentration":false,"flavor":"The greatest evils amount unchallenged. Through fear, they fester.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d6 \\+ 1\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"This spell's **Expound** trait cannot be activated and may only target one creature. The amount of ST recovery granted from this spell is doubled.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 30 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":151000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"uuJ6l1OcQV8KvYlE","name":"Empathic Barrier","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/defensive/shield-barrier-deflect-gold.webp","system":{"description":"You grant up to two target creatures within range the following benefits:\n\n* **Excoriate.** When an attack hits the affected creature, the attacker is dealt **1d8 psychic damage**.\n\n* **Hesitate.** After at least one attack hits each of the affected creatures, this spell is *upgraded* for all affected creatures until this spell ends. When an affected creature is attacked while this spell is upgraded, the attacker must take an additional action to make the attack.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 1d8.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** This spell's range becomes 60 feet.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** This spell may target an additional creature.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"The weight of action is impressed upon the wicked.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 1d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"This spell's range becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"This spell may target an additional creature.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"1d8","damageType":"psychic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":55000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"uvPd4c495FAyAuu3","name":"Planar Threadline","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-spiral-white.webp","system":{"description":"If your initiative partner is targetable and within range, they may teleport to an unoccupied space within your Reach. Afterwards, your initiative partner may take an action to make a weapon attack.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make a weapon attack.\n\nBoth of these attacks deal an additional **6d6 force damage** to their respective targets on a hit.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** You teleport to your initiative partner's previous position when they teleport.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Behind the weave is someone plucking the strings.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"You teleport to your initiative partner's previous position when they teleport.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"6d6","damageType":"force","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":163000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"vKnuug7RbMLHUyKh","name":"Carve Essence","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-body-life-soul-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You choose a creature you are aware of within range and **perceive** them until this spell ends, negating the **Concealed** condition trait of invisible or other features. \n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make a weapon attack. The attack gains the following benefits:\n\n* The attack's range is the range of this spell.\n\n* The attack may target the chosen creature even if the targeting path is obstructed.\n\n* All of the attack's damage is converted to **necrotic**.\n\n* If the attack hits, it deals an additional **9d8 necrotic damage** to the target.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 3d8.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"1 Turn","concentration":false,"flavor":"You call upon the souls around you, draw one forth, and strike true.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 3d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"The range of this spell becomes 60 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"9d8","damageType":"necrotic","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":146000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"vN6yS6BGQibtCEZn","name":"Errant Angle","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/triangle-glow-purple.webp","system":{"description":"You push a target within range 5 feet away from you.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make a weapon attack. If the attack hits, it deals an additional **3d8 slashing damage** to the target.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 2d10.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** After the target is pushed, they become prone.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"Reach","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"The truth of position cut to ribbons.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 2d10.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"After the target is pushed, they become prone.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"3d8","damageType":"slashing","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":56000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"wTsGXh1fDL8M1Hgs","name":"Enthralling Performance","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/mask-yellow-orange.webp","system":{"description":"All creatures in a 30 foot cube originating at a target location within range must make a **Will** saving throw. On a failure, an affected creature is charmed by you and incapacitated until this spell ends. A creature immune to being charmed is unaffected by **Enthralling Performance**.\n\n**Enthralling Performance** effects have the **Out of It** condition trait, which means they end early for a creature if it takes any damage or if they are within another creature's Reach and that creature takes an action to shake them out of their stupor.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 3rd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** When charmed by this spell, a creature is also stunned.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** The side length of the cube increases by 15 feet.","levelLabel":"3rd Circle","spellLevel":4,"heightenedCircle":4,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"cube","shapeSize":"30 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"You hold a captive audience, awestruck by the sheer wonder of it all.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Will","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"When charmed by this spell, a creature is also stunned.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"The side length of the cube increases by 15 feet.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":152000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"wcU1h4hCc3ouagd3","name":"Electric Tomb","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/debuff-energy-snare-purple-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You cause a target within range to make a basic **Will** saving throw to resist **4d8 lightning damage**. Additionally, if the target moves out of its current space before this spell ends, it is dealt an additional **4d8 lightning damage**.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** Both of this spell's damage rolls increase by 4d8.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** This spell's damage ignores DBs.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"occult","spellLists":["occult"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"60 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":false,"flavor":"You enshackle an enemy with filamentary lightning.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Will","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"Both of this spell's damage rolls increase by 4d8.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"This spell's damage ignores DBs.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"4d8","damageType":"lightning","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":112000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"xBdFnteMpd15kO4h","name":"Lifelink","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-large-white.webp","system":{"description":"You cause up to four creatures within range to become *lifelinked* with each other until this spell ends. If this spell ends for one lifelinked creature, it ends for all creatures lifelinked with them. All damage dealt to one or more lifelinked creatures is redirected to be evenly divided amongst all creatures lifelinked with this spell.\n\nAdditionally, if a lifelinked creature makes a saving throw or multiple simultaneously, all of their lifelinked creatures make the saving throw. The best total amongst the saving throws made is used for all lifelinked creatures, and all lifelinked creatures are affected by the success or failure effects caused by the saving throw.\n\nLastly, at the start of a lifelinked creature's turn, that creature **regains 5d4 \\+ 5 ST**.\n\n***Heightening.*** When cast at 6th Circle, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* This spell's ST recovery die becomes 6d4 \\+ 6\\.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** You target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"5th Circle","spellLevel":6,"heightenedCircle":6,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"As threads catch in the light, bind them.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery die becomes 6d4 \\+ 6\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"You target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":199000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"xHFbycOELRYVywjD","name":"Earthquake","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/earth/projectile-stone-landslide.webp","system":{"description":"You cause the earth in a 100 foot radius sphere originating from a target location within range to fold and tremor for the duration of this spell.\n\nUntil this spell ends, all of the following effects occur simultaneously:\n\n* **Difficult Terrain.** All surfaces in the area are considered to be difficult terrain.\n\n* **Tremors.** At the end of your turn, every creature standing in a surface space in the area must make a **Poise** saving throw, falling prone on a failure.\n\n* **Additional Effect.** When you cast this spell and as an action on your future turns until this spell ends, you can cause one of the following effects to occur:\n\n  * **Building Collapse.** A building in the area collapses, potentially trapping any creature inside. All creatures become restrained under a pile of rubble, taking any falling damage the rubble would have taken based on the maximum height of the building. A STR effort check against your spell save DC may be used to escape or help a creature escape.\n\n  * **Fissure.** A fissure 20 feet wide, 60 feet long, and 60 feet deep erupts in this spell's area. A creature on those spaces falls into the fissure and takes the appropriate falling damage.\n\n  * **Landslide**. A cliff or overhang of earth in the area collapses, and slides downhill. All creatures standing atop the crumbling surface or caught in the wake of the avalanche of earth are carried off in some direction, potentially outside of this spell's area.\n\n\\\\This spell may take on other effects as well, depending on the surrounding terrain. When this spell ends, all modifications made to the terrain with this spell remain.","levelLabel":"6th Circle","spellLevel":7,"heightenedCircle":7,"spellList":"primal","spellLists":["primal"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"2 actions","range":"300 feet","shape":"sphere","shapeSize":"100 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"You awaken the ancient words commanding the formation of continents back into speaking tongue.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"Poise","heighteningOptions":[],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":211000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"xTHAaIrbMjr4YVFr","name":"Dispel","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/symbols/ring-circle-smoke-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You target creature or persistent magic (as defined by the Sense Magic action) within range and cause an effect depending on its type:\n\n* **Creature.** You destroy all spell effects affecting the target up to and including 1st Circle.\n\n* **Persistent Magic.** If the persistent magic is created by a 1st Circle spell or below, it is destroyed.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** The maximum spell Circle this spell can end increases by one.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** You make a spellcasting combat check and set the maximum spell Circle this spell can end to either its current value or \\[(the spellcasting check's total \\- 10\\) / 2\\], whichever is higher. **Dispel** cannot end 7th Circle spell effects.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** When targeting a creature, you learn which spells are affecting the creature. You may then selectively end spells of your choosing and leave the remaining intact.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"arcane","spellLists":["arcane"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"When you ascend the Circles of magic, your enemies must follow.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"The maximum spell Circle this spell can end increases by one.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"You make a spellcasting combat check and set the maximum spell Circle this spell can end to either its current value or \\[(the spellcasting check's total \\- 10\\) / 2\\], whichever is higher. **Dispel** cannot end 7th Circle spell effects.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"When targeting a creature, you learn which spells are affecting the creature. You may then selectively end spells of your choosing and leave the remaining intact.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":48000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"xbEBvgg0jAb3Q3ty","name":"Leyline Jaunt","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/movement/portal-vortex-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You teleport any number of target creatures within range to a place you know that satisfies the below requirements:\n\n* **Coplanar.** The place must be on the same plane of existence as you are.\n\n* **Leyline Knot.** The place must be a *leyline knot* that you know, an intangible phenomena that can be created through the casting of a 7th Circle spell. The GM determines where and how many leyline knots already exist.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** You may ignore the **Coplanar** requirement.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** You may ignore the **Leyline Knot** requirement.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above)** The casting time of this spell becomes 6 actions, and these actions may be taken across two consecutive rounds.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 minute","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"The rapids of reality bubble up and invite a dive.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"You may ignore the **Coplanar** requirement.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"You may ignore the **Leyline Knot** requirement.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"The casting time of this spell becomes 6 actions, and these actions may be taken across two consecutive rounds.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":180000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yDdbEm3XMZRIwpIQ","name":"Double Jump","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/movement/trail-streak-impact-blue.webp","system":{"description":"You grant up to three target creatures within range basic Jumping mobility until this spell ends.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 2nd, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** You instead grant advanced Jumping mobility to all affected creatures.\n\n* **(+3 CHA and above, Repeatable)** You target an additional creature within range.","levelLabel":"2nd Circle","spellLevel":3,"heightenedCircle":3,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"30 feet","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"10 Minutes","concentration":true,"flavor":"It really is that simple.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"You instead grant advanced Jumping mobility to all affected creatures.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"},{"text":"You target an additional creature within range.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":"+3 CHA and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":109000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yHju0A8WHbrt2YWf","name":"Tempering Flame","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/fire/dagger-rune-enchant-flame-orange.webp","system":{"description":"You make a weapon attack.\n\n**Spellstrike.** You may take an additional action when this spell begins to make another weapon attack.\n\nBoth attacks have the following effects:\n\n* **If it hits,** the attack's damage is converted to **fire damage** and deals an additional **1d8 fire damage** to the target.\n\n* **If both attacks hit**, you may choose to extend the duration of this spell to 10 minutes and concentrate on it. If you do, you gain the following effects:\n\n  * Whenever you hit with a weapon attack before this spell ends, you convert all of the attack's damage to **fire damage**.\n\n  * The range of your melee weapon attacks is increased by 5 feet.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 1st, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's damage roll increases by 1d6.\n\n* **(+3 INT and above)** While you are concentrating on this spell, your weapon attacks have their critical hit threshold reduced by 1\\.\n\n* **(+3 WIS and above)** While you are concentrating on this spell, the increase in range of your melee weapon attacks becomes 15 feet.","levelLabel":"1st Circle","spellLevel":2,"heightenedCircle":2,"spellList":"divine","spellLists":["divine"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"None","shape":"circle","shapeSize":"5 feet","duration":"Instantaneous","concentration":false,"flavor":"Through effort alone greatness can be realized.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's damage roll increases by 1d6.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""},{"text":"While you are concentrating on this spell, your weapon attacks have their critical hit threshold reduced by 1\\.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 INT and above"},{"text":"While you are concentrating on this spell, the increase in range of your melee weapon attacks becomes 15 feet.","repeatable":false,"attributeRequirement":"+3 WIS and above"}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"1d8","damageType":"fire","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":93000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yqRR7lZxwUj6MKdK","name":"Hypeline","type":"spell","img":"icons/magic/control/energy-stream-link-large-teal.webp","system":{"description":"You cause both you and a target initiative partner within range to **regain 4d8 \\+ 4 ST** and add 15 feet of your Speeds until this spell ends. Additionally, a *hypeline* appears as a 5 foot wide line whose endpoints are your location and the target's location. As you and your target move, the endpoints of the hypeline move along with. If a hypeline passes through a creature, they **regain 4d8 \\+ 4 ST**. A creature cannot be affected by this spell more than once.\n\n***Heightening.*** For each additional Circle above 4th, choose one of the enhancements below:\n\n* **(Repeatable)** This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d8 \\+ 1\\.","levelLabel":"4th Circle","spellLevel":5,"heightenedCircle":5,"spellList":"harmonic","spellLists":["harmonic"],"prepared":false,"castingTime":"1 action","range":"60 feet","shape":"line","shapeSize":"Variable","duration":"1 Turn","concentration":false,"flavor":"Call now for immediate results.","attackType":"","savingThrowType":"","heighteningOptions":[{"text":"This spell's ST recovery roll increases by 1d8 \\+ 1\\.","repeatable":true,"attributeRequirement":""}],"conditionsApplied":[],"damage":"","damageType":"","injuring":false,"healing":null,"summons":null,"discharge":null},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":179000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
